Commentary: Beaten! Swinging delivery to start the innings. A jaffa from Rabada. A length ball on the fourth stump line. Agarwal goes hard with his push but is beaten to due to the away swing.
On the pads this time, Agarwal looks to tuck it on the leg side but the ball takes an inside edge and goes towards fine leg for a couple. India and Agarwal are underway.
Outside off, not much bounce on the surface. Agarwal shoulders arms.

FOUR! First boundary! Fuller length ball around off, Agarwal leans into the shot and guides it through backward point and gully. The ball races to the third man fence. Rabada is not happy with that effort from Dane Piedt at backward point.
Length delivery outside off, Agarwal leaves it alone.
Gets the line wrong this time as Rabada bowls it on the pads on a good length, Agarwal looks to flick but misses.
Ngidi starts with a fullish length ball around off, Rohit pushes it towards mid off.
Rohit is up and running now, with a single. A good length ball on middle, he tucks it towards mid-wicket and gets a run.
In the channel outside off this time, Mayank is not chasing after these.
Slightly fullish length around off, Agarwal pushes it towards point.
Beaten! Good delivery that one from Ngidi. He dishes out the ball in the channel outside off and has Mayank going for the drive. No edge though.
Outside off, Agarwal looks to defend it out but is squared up as he gets a thick outside edge which goes to gully on the bounce.
Beauty! Rohit is beaten now. A ball in the channel that shapes away from the bat as Rohit fiddles with it away from the body.
Good length outside off, this time Rohit makes a leave.
Good length ball angled into the batter, Rohit looks to flick but misses to get hit high on the pads. A stifled appeal follows but nothing from the umpire.
On middle, Rohit blocks it out.
Another good delivery from Rabada. It pitches around off and shapes away again. Rohit looks to punch but is beaten due to the away movement.
Length ball outside off, Sharma makes a leave this time.
Outside off to start the fresh over. Agarwal leaves it alone.
Gets closer to the off pole but not enough to make Agarwal play for it. Agarwal makes another leave.
Three leaves in the row now. Another ball outside off, Agarwal has no business with it.
That kept low! This is on a good length area again, closer to the off pole as well. Agarwal looks to defend but is beaten.
Another leave. This is outside off, Agarwal shoulders arms.
On the leg stump line this time. The ball goes further down the leg side. Agarwal looks to flick but cannot get any bat on the ball.
Fullish length ball on middle, Rohit blocks it towards mid on.
Length outside off, Rohit leaves it alone. Rabada is unable to make the batsman play.
Slightly short on the body, Rohit tucks it towards mid-wicket and takes a run.

FOUR! Nicely done! Shortish length ball outside off, Agarwal guides it through the slip cordon and gully. The ball races to the third man fence. De Kock chases after the ball from the slips but the ball wins the race.
On middle, Agarwal looks to flick but is hit high on the pads. Rabada makes a surprising appeal but nothing from the umpire.

OUT! Rabada strikes! A brilliant low catch from Dean Elgar. Rabada dishes out a good length ball outside off. Agarwal after getting a boundary a couple of balls ago chases it outside off and gets a thick outside edge as the ball shapes a hint away. The ball goes low to Dean Elgar at third slip. He pouches it just above the turf to send Agarwal packing. The umpire checks for the no ball but it is all good there. Exactly the kind of start the visitors' would've hoped for.
WOW! How did that miss the edge and the timber! A beauty! Length ball around off, Rohit lunges a hint to block but is beaten. Lucky there is the Hitman.
Outside off, this time Rohit leaves it alone.
Another ball which is way outside off, Sharma makes another leave.
Another one. Length ball outside off, Rohit shoulders arms.
Gets closer to the batsman on a good length, Rohit taps it towards cover.
A leave to end the over as Ngidi bowls it outside off.

Huge appeal but that looked like it will miss the leg stump. Rabada bowls it around off and angles it into the batter. Pujara looks to defend but is beaten to get hit on the back pad. Rabada appeals but the umpire shakes his head. The Ball Tracker arrives and confirms that the umpire made a perfect call as the ball was going over the stumps.
Nicely bowled! In the channel outside off, Pujara leaves it alone.
On middle, Pujara blocks it out solidly.
Outside off, Pujara has no business with it as he shoulders arms.
Around off, Pujara guides it with the angled bat towards gully.

Rabada is looking to hit the timber as he bowls another full ball on the stumps. Pujara this time goes for the flick but misses again. The ball hits the pads and Rabada makes another appeal but not given.
Length around off, Rohit pushes it back to the bowler who can't make a stop and the ball goes to mid off.
Around off, Rohit bunts it onto the pitch.
A rare poor ball in the session but Rohit misses out. Ngidi bowls it way outside off and Rohit chases after it away from the body. Can't make any connection.
Outside off again, this time Sharma makes a leave.
In the channel outside off, it is left alone.

FOUR! First one from Rohit's bat. Not the best way to get it but he won't mind. Length ball outside off, Rohit goes after it again and gets a thick outside edge which flies between third slip and the gully region. The ball races to the third man fence.
On middle, Pujara blocks it out.
Outside off, left alone.

OUT! Three reds! Pujara has to go. Rabada is on a roll. A superb incoming ball. Rabada was aiming the timber from the start. He dishes out a length ball around off, the ball comes in with the angle as Pujara comes forward to defend but the ball swings in and hits Pujara on the pads. Rabada and South Africa make a loud appeal but the umpire, surprisingly, says not out. Rabada signals for the DRS straightaway. The skipper obliges and gets the decision overturned as the Ultra Edge shows no bat and the Ball Tracker shows three reds, hitting the middle stump. Pujara has to depart. A successful review from South Africa. A perfect start for the Proteas in this Test after losing the toss.
A bumper to welcome the Indian skipper. Kohli does well to duck under it.
Outside off this time, Virat leaves it alone.
Around off, Kohli makes a solid block.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Good length ball outside off, Rohit taps it towards cover and takes a run.
Around off, Kohli defends it towards cover.
Around off and middle, Kohli defends it out watchfully.
Around off, Kohli blocks it out.
Length ball around off, Kohli bunts it towards point.
Fuller on off, Rohit strokes it straight to mid off.

NOT OUT! A big inside edge saves Rohit. Rabada has to wait for his third. Length ball around off which again comes in with the angle. Rohit looks to block but gets an inside edge onto the pads. Rabada appeals and the umpire agrees instantly. Rohit signals for the 'T' straightaway. Here comes the Ultra Edge and there is a huge inside edge. Rohit survives, thanks to the DRS.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Full ball on middle, Rohit pushes it towards mid on.
Outside off, Rohit makes a leave.
Beaten! A superb ball again. It is on a good length and closer to the off pole. Rohit has to play at it. He does so but the ball beats the outside edge and goes behind.
Fuller outside off, Kohli guides it towards point.
FOUR! Boundary no. 1 for the Indian skipper. Nortje bowls a full ball on the pads, Kohli flicks it nicely down the leg side and the ball races to the fine leg fence.
On the pads this time, Virat looks to flick but can't get bat on ball and is hit on the pads.
Fuller length around off,  Virat tucks it towards mid on.
FOUR! Another ball on the pads and Kohli is not going to miss out. He again helps it fine down the leg side to get another boundary.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Outside off this time, Rohit blocks it off the back foot towards the slip cordon. It goes off the outside edge to the third slip but on the bounce.

FOUR! Nicely done! Rabada must be tired after bowling a long spell. He goes for the bumper but it is down the leg side. Rohit goes back and pulls it but the ball hits the glove and tickles to the fine leg fence.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Outside off, left alone.
Another ball outside off, Rohit makes another leave.
Fuller ball around off, Kohli drives it through covers for a quick couple.
Length ball around off, Kohli taps it towards point.
On middle, Kohli punches it firmly towards mid on.

Around off, Kohli taps it towards point and calls for a run. Rohit obliges and takes off. But Hamza from the slip cordon hares at the ball and has a shy at the striker's end and misses that. Could've been a risky run that one.
On middle, Rohit keeps it out.
Outside off, left alone.
Ngidi starts with a ball on the pads, Kohli looks to nudge it fine but can't make proper connection. The ball goes to Klaasen on the bounce.
Length ball angled into the batter, Kohli looks to tuck it towards square leg but the ball goes off the gloves there. They cross.

FOUR! Not a proper connection but a boundary for Rohit nonetheless. A short ball from Ngidi this time, Rohit goes back looking to pull. The ball hits the upper part of the bat and goes over mid-wicket.
Outside off, Rohit looks to defend initially but then decides against it. But he is late in the decision and the ball takes the bottom edge and goes towards gully.
Beaten! A poor shot as Rohit went chasing after that outside off ball. Slightly fuller ball which comes in and beats the inside edge of Rohit's bat.
Around off this time, Rohit tucks it towards mid on for a couple of easy runs.
The batsman lets the ball go outside his off stump.
Loose from the Indian skipper. Nortje bowls it full outside off, Kohli chases after it away from the body but is beaten.

OUT! LBW! UMPIRE'S CALL!  Nortje has got the big fish as his first Test victim and what a massive wicket it is, Virat Kohli. A length ball which comes in with the angle into the right-hander. Kohli looks to go for the on drive but the ball sharply jags back in to beat the bat. It hits the pad and Nortje makes a loud appeal. The umpire raises his finger instantly. Kohli goes for the chat regarding the DRS with Rohit and then goes for it. Here comes the Ball Tracker, and it shows that the ball is clipping the leg stump. Which means Kohli has to walk back. A superb set up from Nortje. Rabada was doing the same and Nortje has got the huge wicket of the Indian skipper with that same plan.
Fuller ball on the pads, Rahane tucks it towards mid-wicket.
Fuller around off, Rahane works it through square leg for a quick couple.
Another fuller ball on the stumps, Rahane tucks it nicely through mid on to take another two. Rabada does well to chase down the ball and keep it in the play.
Full delivery around off, Rohit tries to defend it off the front foot and it goes off the bottom edge of his bat towards second slip.
On a length on middle, Rohit flicks it towards the mid-wicket fielder for nothing.
Fullish delivery on middle, Sharma lunges forward and blocks it towards mid on.
Good length delivery outside off, Sharma defends it towards point and wants a single but is sent back by Rahane.
On a length on middle and leg, Rohit looks to flick but misses. Gets hit on the pads and Ngidi appeals but nothing from the umpire.
On middle, defended off the front foot towards the bowler.
Around off, Rahane looks to defend it out but gets an inside edge. The ball goes towards mid-wicket.
On the pads this time, pushed towards mid-wicket.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Fuller ball around off, Rahane strokes it straight to the cover fielder.
Shortish length ball outside off, Rahane taps it straight to covers again.
Shortish length ball outside off, Rahane guides it towards point.

FOUR! Flicked! Rohit is not going to miss out anything on the pads. Ngidi bowls a length ball on middle, the ball goes away with the angle further. Rohit flicks it through mid-wicket to earn a boundary. Top shot but a poor ball too.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Outside off, actually way outside off, Rohit leaves it alone.
Length ball around off, Rohit guides it towards the slip cordon with soft hands.

Fuller ball on the pads, Rohit looks to nudge it towards the leg side but gets an inside edge and the ball races towards the fine leg fence. Deep mid-wicket fielder makes a diving stop before the ball trudges over the fence. A couple taken.
Good length around off, worked towards mid-wicket by Rohit.
Around off, Rahane blocks it out.
Shortish length ball around off, Rahane stands tall and punches it off the back foot to take two. 50 up for India with that couple.
Length ball closer to the off pole, blocked nicely.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Fuller around off, Rahane defends it towards cover.
Length ball outside off, Rahane pushes it off the back foot towards cover.
FOUR! Hammered! Slightly short on the hips of Rohit. He goes back and times the pull shot to perfection as he lofts it over mid-wicket. The ball races to the boundary.
On the pads, Rohit tucks it behind square on the leg side to take a run.
Fuller ball outside off, left alone.
Beaten! Shortish length ball outside off, Rahane chases the ball to get beaten. He need not play shots like these with Lunch just 10 minutes away.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.

FOUR! Soft hands from Rahane gets him his first boundary of the innings. Not a boundary ball that one. It is on a length around off, Rahane looks to defend it with soft hands but the ball takes an outside edge and goes through the slip cordon. The ball races to the third man fence.
Starts with a quicker ball on the pads, Rohit looks to block but is late into the shot and is hit on the pads.
On the stumps again, Rohit blocks it out.

DROPPED! That could've been a wicket in the first over for Linde on debut but Hamza has put it down. Linde bowls it on the pads again, Rohit looks to work it down the leg side but short leg fielder intercepts. The ball goes straight to his hands but does not stick. How costly will that be?
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
On middle, Rohit keeps it out.
Fuller on the pads, worked towards square leg for a single.
Shortish length ball outside off, Rohit looks to punch but the ball hits the bottom part of the bat and goes towards covers.
Superbly done! Nortje bowls it full on the pads of Rohit. He flicks it nicely through mid-wicket. Ngidi chases the ball and saves a run.
Around off, Rahane taps it towards point and takes a quick single.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.

SIX! Not from the middle of the bat but good enough to sail over the fence. A short ball outside off which is aimed at the head of Rohit. RS is not going to duck under it as he attemps the pull shot. However, he can't make the sweetest of connections. He gets a top edge but the ball flies over the deep square leg fence. He shouldn't be playing these shots with the Lunch break around the corner.
Length ball around off, Rohit tucks it towards short mid-wicket. WITH THAT, IT IS LUNCH ON DAY 1.
Starts with a flatter delivery on middle, Rahane defends it off the back foot to the bowler.
Flatter delivery outside off, Rahane camps back and punches it towards the cover region for a single.
Full delivery outside off, Rohit prods forward and defends it towards cover.
FOUR! Brilliant shot! Short ball around off, Rohit rocks back and cuts it nicely towards the deep extra cover region for a boundary. Nortje runs after it to clean it up but fails to do so.
Flighted ball on middle and leg, Rohit looks to sweep but gets hit on the pads. There was a stifled appeal for LBW but nothing from the umpire.
Full delivery on off, Rohit blocks it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Superb from Rahane! Rabada dishes a fullish ball on middle, Rahane flicks it towards the deep mid-wicket region for a boundary.
On a length outside off, Rahane shoulders arms to this one.
Full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes this towards mid on for nothing.

EDGED AND FOUR! Second boundary of the over for Rahane! Good length ball outside off, Rahane looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards second slip on the bounce. Faf over there does not get hold of the ball and it goes into the third man fence.
FOUR! Good shot from Ajinkya! Good length ball outside off, Rahane plays it with an angled bat towards the third man region for the third boundary of the over.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Rahane flicks it to backward square leg and keeps strike for the next over. Good over comes to an end for India.
Short ball outside off, Rahane punches this off the back foot towards the extra cover region for a couple. Anrich comes around from deep cover and cleans it up.
Full delivery outside off, Ajinkya defends it off the front foot.
Flatter delivery around off, Rahane defends it off the back foot.
Fullish delivery on middle, Ajinkya defends it back to the bowler off the front foot.
Another full delivery on middle, Ajinkya defends it off the front foot yet again.
On middle, defended off the front foot.
BEATEN! Excellent delivery from Kagiso Rabada! Bowls a good length ball outside off, Sharma looks to defend it but fails to put any bat on it.
PLAY AND A MISS! Another excellent ball from Rabada. He bowls it on a length swinging away from the batsman around off, Rohit shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball outside off, Sharma shoulders arms to this one.
NO BALL! Excellent delivery though from Rabada! Full length delivery outside off, Rohit looks to push it but misses the ball yet again. Rabada has bowled a probing over so far.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Short ball on middle, Rohit defends it back to the bowler off the back foot.
Good length ball on middle, Sharma defends it off the front foot.
Short ball outside off, Rahane cuts it off the back foot towards the cover region for a single.
Full delivery outside off, Rohit pushes it towards cover.
Short ball outside off, Sharma rocks back and punches this off the back foot towards the cover region for a single.
Full delivery around off, Rahane defends it off the front foot.
Fullish delivery on middle, Rahane flicks it towards mid-wicket.

FOUR! Good shot from Rahane! Linde bowls a short delivery outside the off stump, Rahane camps back and punches this towards the extra cover region for a boundary. The fielder at the cover region had no chance.

EDGED AND FOUR! Rabada has been excellent since the Lunch break! He bowls a full delivery on middle with a little swing on it, Rohit looks to drive but gets an outside edge which goes past the diving fielder and into the third man fence. 100 up for India.
Good length delivery on middle, Sharma looks to defend but gets a bottom edge towards mid-wicket and the batters take a single.
FOUR! Poor ball from Rabada! Good length delivery on the pads, Rahane flicks it nicely towards the fine leg region for a boundary.
Played to the mid-wicket region by the batsman.
Full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Rabada dishes out a full ball on middle, Rahane flicks it away to the mid-wicket region for another boundary. 13 runs have come off this over.
Good length ball on middle, Rohit defends it off the back foot to mid off.
Full delivery outside off, Rohit lunges forward and pushes this towards the mid off region.

FOUR! 11TH FIFTY FOR SHARMA IN TESTS! Rohit continues to make merry since he started opening in Tests. Nortje bowls a full delivery on middle, Rohit drives this beautifully towards the mid off region for a boundary. He raises his bat and soaks in the applause. He started edgy but has started to look comfortable now.
Pushed to the cover region by the batsman.
Full delivery on middle, Rohit pushes this towards the bowler where Nortje makes a good sliding stop.
Good length ball on middle, Sharma defends it out. The session run rate for India has been 6.29 so far.
Good length ball on off, Rahane lunges forward and defends it towards cover.
Good length delivery down the leg side, Rahane looks to flick but misses it completely.
Short delivery on middle, Rahane flicks it towards the fine leg region for a couple. The fielder comes around from deep square leg and cleans it up.
Full delivery on middle, Ajinkya drives it to mid off for nothing.
Good length ball on middle, Rahane looks to defend it but it goes off the inside edge onto the pitch.
On a length around off, Ajinkya attempts to defend but it goes off the inside half towards square leg. Rahane wants a couple but they decide against it and rightly so.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Rahane defends it off the front foot towards mid on.
On a length outside off, Ajinkya lunges forward and defends it towards the cover fielder.
BEATEN! Poor shot from Rahane! Good length ball outside off, Rahane looks to push it off the back foot but gets beaten. Rahane could have left this one alone.
On a length on middle, Ajinkya defends it back to the bowler off the front foot.
Good length ball on middle, Ajinkya rocks on his back foot and blocks it out.
Back of a length delivery on off, Ajinkya defends it out towards the off side.
Full delivery on middle, Rohit defends it off the front foot.
Flighted ball on middle and leg, Sharma lunges forward and defends it towards mid on.

Flighted delivery on middle, Rohit dances down the track and flicks it towards mid-wicket and takes off for a single. Quinton de Kock though slides and makes an excellent stop forcing Rohit to return back to the crease.
BEATEN! Quicker delivery outside off, Rohit looks to play the cut but does not put any bat on it.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Full delivery on middle, Sharma defends it back to the bowler off the front foot.
Good length ball on off, Rahane defends it off the front foot towards the point region.
Full delivery on off, Rahane pushes it towards the mid off region.
On a length on middle, Ajinkya defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
Fullish delivery around off, Rahane prods forward and blocks it off the front foot towards cover.
FOUR! Beautiful from Rahane! Short delivery outside off, Rahane pushes this off the back foot towards the cover region for a boundary. He moves to 47 with that shot.
Back of a length delivery around off, Rahane guides it towards the gully fielder.
Full delivery on the pads, Sharma looks to flick but gets  hit on the pads. There is a stifled appeal but it is going way down the leg side.
Floated ball on middle, Rohit pushes this off the front foot towards mid on.
On middle, defended.
Flighted ball on middle, Sharma defends this off the front foot.
Full delivery on the pads, Sharma flicks it towards the fine leg region for a couple. The fielder comes around and cleans it up.

FOUR! Nicely played! Flighted delivery on middle, Sharma prods forward and flicks it away with his wrists and into the mid-wicket fence. Quinton hares after it but fails to stop the ball from going into the fence.
On a length on middle and leg, Rahane camps back and defends it off the back foot.
Good length ball around off, Ajinkya defends it to point off his back foot.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Rahane defends it off the back foot to the bowler.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Rahane flicks it towards the square leg region for a single.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
FOUR! Beautiful shot from Rohit! Full delivery outside off, Rohit lunges forward and drives this past the cover fielder for a boundary.
The batsman has flicked the ball off his pads. One run added to the total.
FOUR! Nicely played! Floated ball on middle, Rohit plays it with his wrists and flicks it towards the mid-wicket region for another boundary.
BEATEN! Flatter delivery outside off keeping a little low, Rohit looks to cut it but gets beaten due to the low bounce on it.
Full delivery outside off, Sharma pushes this towards the mid off region and brings up the 100-run partnership between the two. A much needed one for India.
Flighted delivery on middle, Ajinkya looks to flick but gets a leading edge towards the bowler who collects it on the bounce.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Full delivery on middle, Rohit flicks it towards the short mid-wicket fielder for nothing.
FOUR! Powerfully played from Sharma! Full delivery around the off stump line, Sharma drives this uppishly past the silly mid off fielder and into the long off fence.
Good length delivery on off, Sharma defends it off the front foot towards the point region.
FOUR! Poor ball fromk Ngidi! Bowls a full delivery on the pads, Rohit does not miss out on these freebies and flicks it away to the fine leg region for a boundary.
Good length ball outside off, Sharma lets the ball go to the keeper.
Good length ball outside off, Sharma leaves this ball alone.
Piedt starts with a full delivery on middle and leg, Rahane flicks it towards short mid-wicket.
On off, defended

FIFTY! 21st fifty for Rahane in Tests! He gets there by flicking this full delivery on middle towards the long on region for a single. This has been an excellent innings from the vice captain. He came in at a time when India were in trouble and he has played with complete ease on this pitch.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Full delivery on middle, Sharma defends it off the front foot.
Loopy ball on middle, Rohit flicks it towards the square leg region for a single.
Good length delivery on middle, Sharma looks to defend but it goes off the bottom edge of his bat and onto the pads.
Played to mid-wicket region by the batsman.
On a length on middle, Sharma lunges forward and defends it off the front foot.
Full delivery outside off, Rohit prods forward and drives this towards the cover region for a single. With that, 150 is up for India.
Good length ball outside off, Ajinkya leaves this ball alone.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Rahane pushes this to the mid on fielder for nothing.
Full delivery on middle, Sharma lunges forward and defends it towards short leg.
Floated ball on off, Rohit flicks it towards long on and crosses over for a single.

FOUR! Wonderful shot!  Full delivery outside off, Rahane leans forward and drives this towards the cover-point region for another boundary. The fielder runs after it to try and clean it up but the ball wins the race.
Driven through mid-off by the batsman.
Full delivery outside off, pushed towards cover where Elgar misfields. The ball goes towards mid off where Linde mops up the ball. A single taken.
SIX! Stand and deliver! Flighted fuller ball outside off, Rohit just stands and lofts this over the long off region for the first maximum of the innings.
Good length ball outside off, Ajinkya lets this ball go to the keeper.
On a length ball on off, Rahane defends it off the front foot towards cover.
On middle, defended off the front foot to the bowler.
On a length outside off, Ajinkya shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball on the fourth stump line, Ajinkya leaves this ball alone.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Rahane defends it out off the back foot.
Full delivery on middle, Rohit lunges forward and defends it off the front foot.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.

SIX! Mgnificent shot from Sharma! Flighted ball around off, Rohit lofts this over the long on region for another maximum. From the first look of it, it did not look like it had enough on it but the ball went deep into the stands.
Loopy ball on middle, Rohit flicks it towards the leg side for a single.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Full delivery on middle, Ajinkya defends it off the front foot.
Good length delivery on middle, Rohit flicks this towards square leg and takes a single. He wants a couple but it is not there.
On a length on middle, Rahane defends this off the back foot towards the bowler.
Good length ball outside off with a little bit of swing on it, Rahane shoulders arms to it. Klaasen behind the stumps fails to collect it cleanly.
FOUR! Good shot! Full delivery on middle, Rahane drives this uppishly but past the mid on fielder for a boundary.
Full delivery outside off, Rahane drives this nicely yet again but finds Bavuma at cover this time who makes a tumbling stop.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Full delivery outside off, Sharma pushes this ball off the front foot towards the cover region for a couple. Moves on to 94 now does Rohit.
Full delivery on off, Rohit pushes this off the front foot towards the mid off region for a single.
Full toss on middle, Rahane pushes this towards the mid on region for a single.

SIX! 6th century for Sharma in Tests! What a way to get there! Excellent innings from the Hitman! Flighted ball outside off, Rohit lofts this nonchalantly over the long off region for a maximum. Third century in this series and he lifts his bat and gets a hug from Rahane as he soaks in the applause.
The batsman has flicked the ball off his pads.
Full delivery on middle, Rohit defends it off the front foot.
Full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes it back to the bowler.
On a length on off, Sharma defends it off the front foot towards the cover region.
Good length delivery on middle, Ajinkya prods forward and defends it back to the bowler.
Good length delivery on middle, AR rocks on his back foot and blocks it out.
Full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes it towards the mid on region.
Fullish length, pushed to covers by Rahane. Maiden over for Rabada.
Full delivery on middle, Sharma pushes it to mid on and takes a single.
Loopy ball on off, Rahane defends it off his front foot towards cover.
Flighted ball on off, Rahane comes down the track and pushes it to silly mid on.

SIX! Now Rahane joins the act! Piedt bowls a flighted delivery outside off, Rahane puts on his dancing shoes and lofts this over the bowler's head for his first maximum of the game. The maximum brings 150-run stand between the two Mumbai lads. Magnificent partnership.
Full delivery on middle, Ajinkya defends it out.
Driven through mid-on by the batsman.
Fullish delivery outside off, Rohit drives this towards the mid off region.
On a length on middle, Rohit blocks it towards mid on.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Rohit defends it off the back foot.
Short ball on middle, Rohit plays the pull shot towards the deep mid-wicket region for a single.
Short ball on middle, Rahane rocks on his back foot and pulls it in front of square for a couple. The fielder runs in and cleans it up.
Another short delivery on middle and leg, Rahane pulls it towards Nortje at backward square leg and crosses over for a single.
Full delivery outside off, Rahane lunges forward and pushes it towards the mid off region for a single.
Flighted ball on the pads, Rohit flicks it towards the fine leg region for a couple. Ngidi runs in from deep square leg and cleans it up.
Full delivery on middle, Rohit defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
The batsman works it down the leg side. Two runs added to the total. 200 up for India.
Floated ball on middle, Sharma defends it off the front foot.
Flatter delivery on middle and leg, Sharma pushes it towards silly mid on.
Good length ball outside off, Rahane lets this ball go to the keeper.
BEATEN! Beautifully bowled! Good length ball on middle and off, Rahane looks to defend but is cut in half. The ball goes to the keeper. It took a long time coming though for a ball to miss the bat.
On a length on middle, Rahane defends this off the back foot.
Fullish delivery on off, Rahane defends this off the front foot towards the cover region.
On a length outside off, Ajinkya shoulders arms to this one.
Back of a length delivery around off, Ajinkya defends it off the back foot.
Full delivery outside off, Rohit lunges forward and defends it towards the cover region for a single.
Full delivery on the pads, Rahane flicks it towards the deep square leg region for a couple. Ngidi comes around and cleans it up.
Full delivery on middle, Ajinkya defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
The batsman shoulders arms to let that one through.
Flighted ball around off, Rahane prods forward and defends it off the front foot to point and crosses over for a single.
Loopy ball on off, Rohit lunges forward and defends it off the front foot.
On a length on off, Rahane defends it off the back foot towards the square leg region and takes a single.
Good length ball on middle, Rohit flicks it towards square leg for nothing.
On a length on middle, Rohit rocks on his back foot and defends it to the bowler.
Fullish delivery on off, Rohit defends it off the front foot.
Good length delivery on middle, Rohit blocks it out off the back foot.
Back of a length delivery outside off, Rohit camps back on his back foot and defends it out. WITH THAT IT IS TEA ON DAY ONE.
Linde starts with a loosener outside off, Rahane cuts it towards deep cover for a single.
On off and middle, Rohit defends it out off the front foot.
Flighted ball on middle, Rohit is solid in his defense.
This time he bowls a fuller one, almost a yorker, Rohit digs it out.
Flighted fuller ball outside off, Sharma pushes it towards cover.
Around off, Rohit tucks it towards point. Ajinkya wanted a run there but Rohit wasn't interested.
He starts with a fullish length ball on off, Rahane lunges forward to defend.
Bowls a back of a length ball around off, Rahane stands tall to tap it towards cover.
Length ball around off again, Rahane keeps it out with ease.
Too straight this time from Nortje. Rahane tucks it behind square leg for a single.
Full ball on middle, Rohit pushes it straight to short mid-wicket.
Outside edge but it kept low. A fuller length ball outside off. Rohit looks to defend it out but gets a thick outside edge which goes wide of the slip fielder. A single taken.
Flighted fuller ball outside off, RS drives it towards long off for a single.
On middle this time, Rahane flicks it between deep mid-wicket and long on. Nortje from long on gets to the ball with a dive and  stops a couple.
Fires one outside off, Rahane leaves it alone.
Fuller ball on middle stump, Rahane works it towards short mid-wicket.
Around off, it is kept out.
On the pads this time, Rahane finds the short mid-wicket fielder with his flick again.
Length ball on the fourth stump line, Rohit pushes it towards mid on.
Fuller ball outside off, Rohit goes for the drive but gets a thick edge which goes towards point on the bounce.
Around off on a good length, Rohit looks to drive again but the ball goes towards square leg off the inner half of the bat. They take a run.
Fuller ball around off, Rahane keeps it out.
Good length ball on off and middle, tucked towards square leg.
Nortje bowls this way down the leg side, Rahane goes for the flick but misses. Klaasen dives to his left and gets a glove to it. The ball goes behind and the batters take a run.
Outside off, it is left alone.
FOUR! Top shot that one. Linde overpitches this around off and middle, Rahane uses his wrist to whip it through mid on. The ball races to the long on fence.
Fires this one outside off, Rahane shoulders arms.
A quicker one around off, Rahane guides it towards short third man.
Flighted ball around off, Rahane comes down the track and pushes it towards long off for a single.
Full ball on the pads, Rohit whips it towards short mid-wicket who makes a half stop. No runs conceded though.
FOUR! Easy pickings these. Too straight from Nortje. Rohit latches onto it in a flash and whips it off his pads towards the deep square leg boundary.
Length ball around off, Rohit defends it out.
Another ball on the pads, Rohit works it towards deep square leg for a single.
Length ball around off, Rahane pushes it towards mid off.
Slightly short ball around off and middle, Rahane stands tall to bunt it onto the pitch.
Back of a length ball around off, Rahane does well to defend it out.
Rabada starts with a good length ball on middle, Sharma rocks on his back foot and defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on off, Rohit lunges forward and pushes it to the cover region.
On a length outside off, Rohit shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball angling into the batsman, Rohit looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of the bat towards square leg.
Fullish delivery outside off, Sharma pushes it to mid off for nothing.
Good length delivery outside off, Rohit prods forward and defends it to the cover region. Maiden over to start Day 2 from Rabada.
Starts with a full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes it back to the bowler.
Another full delivery on off, Rahane lunges forward and drives this towards mid off.
FOUR! Absolutely glorious says Murali Kartik on air! Nortje bowls a full delivery outside off, Rahane prods forward and creams the cover drive past the fielder and into the fence.
Another full delivery outside off, Ajinkya drives this nicely again but finds Linde at cover this time who dives to make the stop.
Good length ball on off, Rahane pushes it to mid off.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
On a length outside off, Rohit defends it off the back foot towards the point region.
Good length ball on off, Rohit gets on his front foot and defends it out towards mid off.
Good length ball outside off, Rohit Sharma does not fiddle with it and leaves it alone.
On off, left alone by Sharma.
On a length on middle, Sharma rocks on the back foot and blocks it out.

FOUR! Nicely played from Rohit! Not a bad delivery from Rabada but it is just the class of the man! Bowls a fullish delivery on middle, Rohit drives this but it goes off the sticker of his bat and towards mid on region for a boundary. Ngidi runs after it to stop the ball while sliding forward but is unable to do so.
Good length ball on middle, Rahane comes on his front foot and defends it to the cover region.
Another good length ball outside off, Rahane lunges and blocks it out.
OHH! That probably hit a crack or something! Nortje bowls a good length delivery around off swinging away from the batsman, Rahane looks to defend but misses it completely due to the swing on it.
Good length ball delivery on middle, Rahane defends it out.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.

Good length ball on the pads, Rahane looks to flick but misses the ball to get hit on the pads. Nortje appeals but nothing from the umpire as it looked like going down the leg side. The Ball Tracker rolls in and it shows that it was clipping the leg stump.
Good length ball outside off, Sharma blocks it towards the point region and crosses over for a single.
Good length ball outside off, Ajinkya lets the ball go to the keeper.
On a length on middle and leg, Rahane defends this towards the mid on region.

FOUR! Beautiful shot from Ajinkya Rahane! Rabada dishes a full delivery outside off, Rahane strides forward and drives this nicely past the mid off fielder for a boundary. Rahane moves into the 90s now.
On a length outside off, Ajinkya leaves it alone.
On a length outside off, Ajinkya shoulders arms to this one.
Starts with a good length ball on middle, Sharma looks to flick but gets hit on the pads. The players make a stifled appeal for LBW but not given by the umpire. It looked like going above the stumps.
On a length on middle, Rohit looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards mid-wicket.
Good length ball outside off, Rohit on the back foot defends it towards the cover region.

FOUR! Beautiful shot! Good length ball on middle, Rohit plays a Nataraja shot towards the deep mid-wicket region for a boundary. Rabada from deep square leg hares after it but fails to reach it in time. 200-run stand is up between these two.
Good length ball on middle, Rohit defends it off the front foot towards the off side.
On off, Rohit defends this towards mid off.
Good length ball outside off, Ajinkya lets this ball go to the keeper.
Full delivery on off, Rahane drives this beautifully but is well stopped by Rabada on his followthrough.
Good length ball on off, Rahane defends this off the back foot towards the cover fielder.
Full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes it towards the mid on region for a single. Nortje comes across and makes a sliding stop.
Good length ball on off, Rohit defends it off the back foot towards cover.
FOUR! Poorly bowled from Rabada! Bowls a full delivery down the leg side, Rohit just helps it on its way towards the fine leg region for another boundary.
Full delivery on off, Rahane pushes this to mid off for nothing.
On a length around off, Rahane camps on his back foot and defends it to point.
Ngidi bowls a good length ball down the leg side, Ajinkya looks to flick but misses the ball.
On a length on off, Ajinkya defends it towards the point region.
Ngidi dishes a fullish ball on middle, Rahane pushes it back to the bowler.

FOUR! Brilliant shot from Rahane! Shortish delivery outside off, Rahane rocks on his back foot and pushes this through the point region for another simple boundary. Rahane just four runs away from his century. 250 up for India.
Good length delivery on off, Sharma defends it to cover and calls Rahane for a single. Bavuma has a shy at the keeper's end but misses it. It would not have mattered though as Rahane was well in.
Good length ball around off, Rahane defends it towards the off side.
Short delivery aimed at the body, Rahane looks to fend it uncomfortably but gets hit on the ribs. Nasty delivery from Nortje.
Another short delivery on middle, Rahane this time camps back and pulls it towards the square leg region for a couple. The fielder from fine leg comes across and cleans it up.
On a length on middle, Ajinkya defends it off the back foot.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.

FOUR! Poor bowling from Ngidi! South African bowlers have been guilty of bowling some balls down the leg side. Lungi bowls a good length ball on the pads, Rohit flicks it nicely towards the fine leg region for another boundary. Easy picking this for the Hitman.
On a length on middle, Rohit flicks it towards the mid-wicket region for nothing.

FOUR! This is just brilliant from Sharma! It was not a bad delivery from Ngidi but the class of Rohit Sharma is too much to handle. Good length ball outside off, Sharma camps on his back foot and punches this past the cover fielder for another boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries for Sharma! Short delivery outside off, Sharma is on his back foot and guides this past the gully fielder and into the third man fence.
Fullish delivery on middle, Sharma flicks it towards mid-wicket and takes a single.
Good length delivery on middle and leg, Rahane flicks this off his back foot towards backward square leg and moves to 99 with this single.

11TH TEST CENTURY FOR RAHANE! It has been an excellent innings. Good length ball around off, Jinx pushes this towards the cover region for a single. His record in India is not great but this innings will give him a lot of confidence. Gets a hug from Rohit and soaks in the applause. Fourth century in India for Rahane, first since 2016.
The batsman has played it to the point region.
FOUR! Well played from Sharma! Short delivery outside off, Rohit stands back and plays a square cut past the point and gully fielders for another boundary.
BEATEN! Poor shot this! It was not needed after getting a boundary off the previous ball! Nortje bowls a good length ball outside off, Sharma attempts to cut it but fails to get any bat on it.
Full delivery on middle, Sharma pushes this to mid on for nothing.
Another short delivery on middle, Sharma pulls this towards the mid-wicket region for a single.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Rohit flicks it towards the mid-wicket fielder for nothing.
Flatter delivery outside off, Sharma lunges forward and defends it to point.

3rd 150 for Rohit Sharma! Excellent innings from Sharma. Will he score a double ton here? Flighted delivery on middle, Sharma dances down the track and pushes it to mid on for a single. Since taking over as an opener, he has been prolific and has cemented his place in the Indian Test side.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Full delivery on middle, Rahane pushes it back to the bowler.
Played through mid-wicket by the batsman.
Starts with a flatter delivery on the pads, Sharma flicks it towards the fine leg region for a single.
Another flat delivery on the pads, Rahane flicks it off his pads and crosses over for a single. Rahane wants a couple but it is not there.
BEATEN! Flighted delivery outside off which went straight on, Sharma looks to defend it with the spin on it but fails to put any bat on it.
FOUR! Some innovation from Rohit Sharma! Flighted delivery outside off, Sharma goes for the reverse sweep and plays it towards the third man region for a boundary.
Played through mid-wicket by the batsman.
Short ball outside off, Rohit punches this off the back foot towards the off side for a single.
Full delivery outside off, Rohit lunges forward and drives this towards the cover region for a couple. Ngidi comes across from deep cover-point and cleans it up.
Flatter delivery on middle, Sharma flicks it towards the long on region for another single. Runs coming easy for India here.
Fullish delivery on off, Rahane defends this off the front foot to the bowler.
Another full delivery outside off, Rahane defends this off the front foot towards the point region.
Flat delivery on middle, Ajinkya prods forward and defends it out.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
A full ball on middle, Rohit pushes it back to the bowler.
Looped up ball outside off, Rohit guides it wide of the first slip fielder for a single.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
FOUR! Hammered! In the slot for Rahane, he dances down the track and lofts it left of the bowler and into the long off fence. Nicely done.
Stumping missed! That was nicely bowled. Rahane comes forward to defend but the ball turns a hint and beats the bat. It goes to Klaasen behind who can't gather the ball cleanly to stump the batter.
On the pads on a fullish length, pushed towards mid on.
Outside off, Rohit pushes it towards cover and takes a run.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Fuller ball on middle, Rahane comes down the track and flicks, but straight to the short mid-wicket fielder.
Fires this one outside off, Rahane cuts it through point for a single.
Full ball on middle, pushed towards mid on for an easy run.
In the air but just short! A fuller ball, a bit of flight. Rahane just pushes it back to the bowler but uppishly. Soft hands push it was and hence it did not carry.
FOUR! Easy pickings! Just making everyone remember Virender Sehwag. Piedt fires this one outside off on a fullish length, Rohit hammers it with the spin through cover-point for another boundary.
On middle, tucked towards mid-wicket for a run.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
FOUR! Another boundary. This time it is Rahane. He dances down the track, and gets to the pitch of the ball to flick it towards the deep mid-wicket fence.
FOUR! Wow! Rahane comes down the track again to get to the pitch of this ball outside off and lofts it inside out over extra cover to earn another boundary.
On the pads this time, worked towards leg side for a single now.
On off, guided towards gully.
On the pads this time, flicked towards mid-wicket for a run.

OUT! CAUGHT! Finally a wicket. Linde it is, who gets his maiden Test wicket. Linde fires this one just outside off on a good length. Rahane looks to guide it late through the slip region but gets the faintest of edges. Klaasen behind the wicket grabs it nicely. Linde appeals but Rahane is not waiting for the decision as he walks instantly. A top knock from the Mumbai lad comes to an end. First catch for Klaasen in Tests.
A quicker one on middle and leg, Jadeja gets his bat in time to dig it out.
Outside off, Jadeja leaves it alone.
Another ball outside off, it is left alone.
Way down the leg side, Rohit looks to work it down the leg side but misses.
On middle, tucked towards the leg side.
What was that? Probably gets a friendly warning from the umpire as well because of the negative line. Piedt fires this way down the leg side. Rohit leaves it alone.
On the pads on a fuller length, pushed towards mid-wicket for a run.
On middle, RJ lunges forward to defend it out.
Around off, Jadeja is behind the line of the delivery to defend.
Full on the pads, Rohit drives it left of Faf du Plessis at mid on who can't make the stop as the ball goes towards long on for a single.
Outside off, tucked behind square by Jadeja to get off the mark.
Around off, Rohit keeps it out.
FOUR! Crunched! Linde fires this way outside off. Rohit rocks back and cuts it through point for another boundary.
On the pads, worked through mid on for a single.
Full around off, Jadeja eases it through mid on for an easy run.
On the pads, Jadeja looks to push it towards mid-wicket but is hit on the pads. The ball goes towards short mid-wicket and the batters take a run.
FOUR! Highest score for Rohit in Tests. He is on the charge now. Gets a fuller ball in the slot, Rohit creams it through covers for another boundary.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Around off and middle this time, Rohit works it towards mid-wicket for an easy run.
On the pads again, worked towards square leg for another single.
Outside off, defended back to the bowler.
Full and on off, pushed towards mid on.
Down the leg side again, Jadeja looks to flick but misses. Another fumble behind the stumps from Klaasen but no runs taken.
On middle, Jadeja defends it out.
Outside off, Jadeja cuts it through covers for a run.
Outside off, Rohit comes down the track to defend it out.
On middle, Rohit keeps it out.
On middle, tucked towards short mid-wicket.
On off and middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Quicker one this time, Jadeja looks to work it on the leg side but the ball goes towards square leg off the inner half of the bat.

NOT OUT! Pitching outside leg and a review is lost for the Proteas. It looked to be a gamble from the Protea skipper. Piedt bowls a flighted ball, Rohit looks to slog sweep but misses to get hit on the pads. Piedt appeals but the umpire is unmoved. Faf after having a discussion opts for the review. Well, that won't help as the ball has pitched outside leg.
On the pads, worked towards mid on for a run.
FOUR! Fuller ball outside off, Rohit creams another cover drive to add four more runs to his tally.
Outside off, pushed towards cover.
Fuller ball on off, blocked back to the bowler.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Down the leg side this time, Jadeja looks to tickle it fine but misses.
Flatter ball outside off, Jadeja guides it towards point for a run.
Outside off, Rohit punches it through covers for a single.
Rabada starts with a full toss ball outside off, Rohit pushes it uppishly towards Temba Bavuma at covers who fumbles and allows a couple..
Way outside off, Rohit shoulders arms.
Another ball outside off, it is left alone.
Length ball closer to the off pole this time, Rohit looks to defend it out but the ball takes the inner half of the bat and goes behind, just over the stumps.

Short but equally well fielded by Bavuma, surely saved three there. A full ball outside off for Rohit, he creams the cover drive but Bavuma at covers intercepts and makes a half stop. The ball goes towards mid off and a single is taken.
FOUR! First one for RJ. Rabada bowls a juicy full ball on the pads, Jadeja flicks it uppishly to the fine leg fence.
FOUR! Another boundary. Runs are coming thick and fast. Nortje starts with a loosener outside off, Rohit just helps it wide of the gully fielder and the ball races to the third man fence.

FOUR! Nortje is not learning and Rohit is not missing out. Too wide outside off, this time Rohit brings out the cut shot and hammers it to perfection. No chance for anyone to even move. Just 5 away from his first double ton.
Length ball closer to off pole, Rohit taps it through point for a single. A slight fumble there and Jadeja wanted the second run but Rohit sends him back.
Good length around off, Jadeja blocks it off the back foot.
Way down the leg side this time. Jadeja looks to flick. Klaasen dive full length to his right to save runs. A single as Rohit hares for a quick single int he form of a bye.
On the pads again, Rohit looks to flick but misses. The ball goes towards square leg for a leg bye.

Almost chopped on! A full ball outside off, Rohit looks to drive it through covers but the ball takes an inside edge and goes to hit the pads. Could've easily gone on to hit the stumps. Jadeja has a word with Rohit.
Closer to the off pole, Rohit this time looks to tap it towards point but gets a bottom edge to the keeper.
A quick couple and just two away from the milestone. A shortish length ball on middle, Rohit works it towards square leg and hares back for a quick couple.

Almost gone! Almost! The Indians in the dressing room do oohs and aahs. Another ball outside off, Rohit looks to defend but gets another inside edge which goes past the stumps. Jadeja hares for another single. Luck favoring Hitman here.

FOUR! Rohit will have to wait to get to his double ton for a while. Good length ball outside off, Jadeja guides it between the slip cordon and the ball races to the third man fence. The boundary brings up the 50-runs stand between the two.
Outside off left alone. LUNCH ON DAY 1.
On the pads, Rohit flicks but finds the short mid-wicket fielder.
Around off, Rohit stands tall to block.
Closer to the off pole on a good length, Rohit keeps it out. Doesn't look to be in a hurry now.
Sprays down the leg side, Rohit goes for the pull but misses as the ball kept a tad bit low.
Shortish length ball on the body, Rohit tucks it off the back foot towards mid-wicket.
Good length ball outside off, Rohit guides it short third man.
Length ball on middle, Jadeja comes forward and defends.
Outside off, luring the batter to go for the drive, RJ leaves it alone.
In the channel outside off, Jadeja is not interested.
Same ball, same shot, I mean no shot.
Finally gets closer to the off pole, Jadeja blocks coming forward.
Another ball outside off, Jadeja makes another leave.

SIX! Maiden double ton. Gets there with a maximum. Just like Virender Sehwag, the man who celebrates his birthday today used to do. The gala time continues for the Hitman. What a series he is having. Got the opening position and he is making it of his own. Gets a good length ball on the hips, he rocks back and hammers a pull over the deep mid-wicket fence to get to the landmark. He got to his century with a six as well.
On the pads, Rohit keeps it out.

SIX! Time for a few more of those then. Ngidi does not learn as he dishes out another shortish length ball on the hips of Rohit. RS transfers his weight on the back foot and pulls it over the deep mid-wicket fence with ease. Six number six.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Outside off, pushed towards point.
Another ball on the leg stump line, Rohit pulls it for a single towards deep mid-wicket.

OUT! CAUGHT! Rohit holes out in the search of quick runs. Magnificent innings comes to an end. A bouncer on the body of Rohit from Rabada. The extra pace of Rabada means that the ball came quicker on the bat and hit the higher part of the willow. Rohit got in the position to pull, does so but finds Ngidi positioned at fine leg. The South African players shake hands with the Hitman as he slowly goes to the pavilion. He got plenty of runs with that shot but the same has brought his downfall. Nonetheless, a magnificent knock Rohit.
On the hips, Saha looks to flick but misses to get hit on the pads.
Around off, pushed towards point.
Shortish length around body, worked behind square for a single.
Outside off, left alone.
On middle, Jadeja defends it out.

EDGY FOUR! Through the second slip and gully fielder. Ngidi can't believe his luck. Faf has just two slips for the new man in. Ngidi lands a ball just outside off, Saha throws his bat at the ball with hard hands. The ball takes the outside edge and flies between the two fielders.
Shortish length ball, Saha stands tall to block.
Outside off, left alone.
Another leave as Ngidi bowls it outside off again.
Outside off, Saha makes another leave.
Good length ball angled into the batter. Saha looks to tuck it around the corner but the ball comes in sharply to hit the pads.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja drives it towards point where Linde dives to his left to save runs.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Nice bumper! Closer to the head of Jadeja who drops his hands and let it pass to the keeper.
Outside off, Jadeja blocks it out.
Outside off this time, Ravindra taps it through covers for a couple of runs.
Good length ball angled away from the batter, Jadeja pushes it towards cover-point.
Loopy ball on middle, tucked behind square leg for a run.
Outside off, Jadeja comes forward to pad the ball away but the ball comes in. However, not enough to hit the pads, goes straight to the keeper.
Full around off, driven straight to the cover fielder.
Fuller again, pushed to covers again.
On middle and off, Jadeja comes forward to block it out.
Fuller ball again, Jadeja looks to block but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
On the pads, Saha looks to work it around the corner but misses to get hit on the pads. The ball rolls towards the leg side and the batters cross for a leg bye.
Landed around off, Jadeja defends it out by coming forward.
Around off, Jadeja pushes it towards covers and looks for a run but is sent back by Saha. The fielder there has a shy at the striker's end but misses, eventually concedes an overthrow.
Good length ball on middle, Saha looks to tap it towards the leg side but gets an inside edge and the ball goes to fine leg for a single.
Around off, Jadeja runs it through point for a couple.
Good length ball angled into the batter but it is wide outside off, RJ shoulders arms.
Around off, Saha blocks.
Outside off, Wriddhi makes a leave now.
On off, Saha comes forward and defends it out.
On the pads, worked towards square leg for a quick run.
Outside off, Jadeja drives it through covers for a couple. The deep point fielder, Nortje was slow to move but eventually got to the ball.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Fuller around off, driven straight to mid off.
Fuller outside off again, Wriddhiman drives but finds the fielder again.
Full around off and middle, punched straight to mid on.
On the pads, Saha works it towards mid-wicket and shouts a no as Jadeja wants a run. The fielder there fumbles but Saha again shouts no.
Fuller on off, driven straight to mid off.
Full outside off, pushed straight to mid off.
Flatter delivery down the leg side, Jadeja looks to flick but misses it completely.
Full delivery on middle, Jadeja flicks it off the front foot past a diving Bavuma at mid on for a single.
Flighted ball on middle, Saha flicks it towards the fine leg region for a couple. Jadeja wants a third but is sent back.
Floated ball on middle, Saha flicks it towards the mid-wicket region for a single.
The batsman flicks it away with a wristy shot.

Short ball outside off, Jadeja rocks back and punches this off the back foot through the cover region for three. Elgar runs after it and makes an excellent sliding stop. The umpires check whether Dean has touched the ropes but he is fine on that front.
Short ball outside off, Jadeja looks to pull it but fails to put anything on it. It was a poor ball from Nortje and one wonders how Jadeja missed that ball.
Good length ball on middle, Jadeja looks to work it to the leg side but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards square leg. The batsmen take a couple.
Good length ball on off, Ravindra camps on his back foot and defends it off the back foot.
On a length outside off, Jadeja shoulders arms to this one.
Fullish delivery outside off, RJ leaves this ball alone to the keeper.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja rocks on his back foot and pushes it towards the cover region.
Loopy delivery outside off with some extra bounce on it, Saha looks to punch it but it goes off the outside edge towards point for a couple.

Full delivery on the middle and leg stump line, Saha looks to paddle sweep this one but it goes off the bat towards square leg for a single. Zubayr Hamza gets to the ball from short leg quickly and has a shy at the keeper's end but misses. It wouldn't have mattered as Jadeja was in time.
Flighted delivery around off, Jadeja looks to defend but it hits the inside edge and hits the pads of Jadeja. There is a stifled appeal for LBW but nothing from the umpire.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Flatter delivery outside off which kept very low, Jadeja does very well to block it out.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Good length ball around off, Saha defends this off the back foot towards the cover region.
Back of a length delivery on the off stump line, Saha defends this off the back foot towards the cover region.
Full delivery on the fourth stump line, Saha lunges forward and drives this to the cover fielder for nothing.
Low full toss aimed the middle stump, Saha does well to flick it towards the mid-wicket fielder.
Good length delivery on the pads, Saha flicks it towards the fine leg region and take a single.
Fullish delivery outside off, Jadeja leaves this ball alone.
Full delivery on middle, Saha defends it back to the bowler off the front foot.
Saha drives this full delivery on off towards covers for a single. 400 up with that run.
Flighted delivery outside off, Jadeja pushes it towards the cover region for nothing.
Floated ball outside off, Jadeja looks to defend but gets hit on the pads. The South African players put in an appeal for LBW but the umpire is unmoved.
Full delivery on the middle pole line, Jadeja flicks it towards square leg.
Loopy ball outside off, Ravindra Jadeja pushes it towards cover. It has been slow going for the hosts since the fall of Rohit's wicket.
BEATEN! Good length ball outside off, Saha looks to cut it but does not put any bat on it.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Saha defends it off the back foot towards the off side.
Full delivery around off, Wriddhiman drives this towards cover for nothing.
Leg bye! Full delivery on the pads, Saha looks to flick but gets hit on the pads. The ball rolls towards the fine leg region for a leg bye.

On a length on off, Jadeja defends it off the back foot towards cover and calls Saha for a single. Bavuma runs in and has a shy at the keeper's end but misses the stumps. Had he hit, it could have been close.
FOUR! Beautiful shot from Saha! Ngidi bowls a full delivery outside off, Saha leans forward and drives this through the cover region for a boundary.
Outside off, left alone.
Flighted delivery on middle, Jadeja pushes it towards the point region.
The batsman drives the ball straight down the ground.
Full delivery on middle, Ravindra defends it out off the front foot.
Full delivery on off, Jadeja pushes it to mid off and crosses over for a single.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Good length ball outside off, Jadeja guides it to the third man region for a couple.
Good length ball on middle and leg, Jadeja looks to flick but gets hit on the pads. There is an appeal for LBW but not given by the umpire. It probably was going down the leg side.
Good length ball on off, Jadeja defends it off the back foot towards the off side.
On a length on off, Jadeja blocks it towards the point region and looks for a single but is sent back by Saha.

FOUR BYES! Good length ball down the leg side, Jadeja looks to flick but misses it. Klaasen also misses it and the ball goes onto the fine leg fence. The Ultra Edge rolls in and it shows that the ball had gone off the glove. Someone from the Protea team asked Umpire Illingworth whether there was bat or glove but he shakes his head.
The batsman lets the ball go outside his off stump.
Short ball outside off, Saha cuts it but straight towards the point fielder.
FOUR! Flighted ball on middle, Saha plays a paddle sweep towards the fine leg region for a boundary.

OUT! BOWLED! Second wicket for Linde! Saha has to depart. Flatter delivery on the middle stump line, Saha looks to defend but it goes between the bat and pad onto the middle stump. Is it too late for South Africa though?
A full ball outside off, Ashwin drives it well but hits the silly point fielder.
Fuller on off, pushed towards mid off.
Shortish length outside off, Ashwin punches it through cover-point for a couple of runs.
Fuller ball, driven straight to covers.
A quicker and a fuller one, pushed towards point.
On off, a solid forward defense from Jadeja
Around off again, Jadeja prods forwards to defend it out.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
First maiden over from Piedt. On off again, RJ looks confused as to drive it or defend but gets a bottom edge and lobs wide of short leg.
Back of a length ball outside off, Ashwin cuts it towards point and takes a quick run.
On middle, it is kept out.
Around the off stump line, Jadeja pushes it back to the bowler.
Flighted delivery around off, Jadeja blocks it out off the back foot.
Fuller ball around the off pole, Jadeja goes for the slog sweep but misses it altogether.
Full outside off, driven towards mid off for a single.
On the pads, RJ looks to defend but is hit on the pads.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Flatter ball around off, pushed towards point.
On off, Jadeja keeps it out.
Fullish on the pads, Jadeja looks to run it fine down the leg side but misses to get hit on the pads.
LEG BYE! On the pads again, Jadeja looks to work it down the leg side again but misses. The ball hits the pads and goes towards square leg for a leg bye.
Fuller ball outside off, Jadeja looks to dig it out but misses.
Shortish length, pushed off the back foot towards mid-wicket by RJ for a single.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Short outside off, Ashwin punches it wide of de Kock at point who dives to get hands on the ball as it goes towards deep mid-wicket. An easy single taken.
FOUR! Going down the leg side, Jadeja just helps it fine down the leg side.

Around off, Jadeja guides it through point and hares for a couple. The throw comes at the non-striker's end but Linde makes no move to collect the ball, the ball goes to long on and an overthrow is taken.
On middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Around middle and leg, Jadeja pushes it wide of the bowler.
Flatter one on the pads, Jadeja looks to flick but misses to get any bat on the ball. The ball hits the pads. A stifled appeal but this was surely going down the leg side.
On the pads, blocked towards short leg.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
On middle, Jadeja dives it towards mid on for nothing. Three maidens in a row from Piedt.
Outside off, Ashwin reaches for the ball to punch it through covers for a single.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Full outside off, Jadeja drives it firmly wide of the mid off fielder for a single.
Around off, Ashwin keeps it out.
Fuller outside off, Ashwin drives it left of the bowler and takes off for a quick run before the mid off gets to the ball.
FOUR! Slog sweep to get closer to his half ton. Outside off, Jadeja fetches the ball from there and slog sweeps it left of the long on fielder to get a boundary.
Fuller ball outside off, Ashwin looks to drive but gets a thick outside edge. The ball goes towards third man. Ashwin gets a couple.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
On middle, Ashwin works it towards mid-wicket for a run.
Fires one closer to off pole. Jadeja looks to cut but misses.
Full toss on the pads, Jadeja pushes it towards long for a single.
FOUR! A full ball on the pads, Ashwin moves a bit across the off stump and sweeps it fine to get his first boundary.
Flighted ball outside off, Jadeja rocks on his back foot and guides this towards the third man region for a couple.
Full delivery on the off stump line, Jadeja pushes it towards the cover region.

13TH FIFTY FOR JADEJA IN TESTS! Flighted ball on the pads, Jadeja looks to sweep but it goes off the edge towards the fine leg region for a couple. Jadeja has improved batting in recent times and this is another instance of him showing his class with the bat. Jadeja does his usual celebration of swinging his bat in the air in celebration.

OUT! CAUGHT! Jadeja walks! Linde, on his debut gets his third wicket. Flighted delivery outside off with extra bounce on it, Jadeja looks to cut but gets an outside edge which Klaasen manages to hold onto it. Jadeja does not even wait for the umpire's decision and walks back to the pavilion. Not much of a celebration from South Africa.

SIX! WHOA! Umesh enters the crease with a bang! First ball and a maximum. Flighted delivery on middle, Umesh gets on his front foot and lofts this over the long on region for a maximum. Umesh has shown in domestic cricket that he can bat and he is showing it here.

SIX! This is brilliant from Umesh! Back-to-back sixes for Yadav! Another flighted delivery on middle, the right-hander stands in his crease and lofts this over the long on region for another maximum. Brilliant cricket from Umesh. Declaration coming soon?
Piedt starts from round the wicket and bowls it on the pads, Ashwin nudges it behind square to get Yadav on strike. The crowd errupts seeing that.
Goes for the slog sweep but misses. It is around middle, Yadav goes for the massive heave but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Outside off, eased for a single through mid off.
The batsman works it down the leg side.

OUT! Stumped! A flighted ball outside off which deceives Ashwin as he comes forward to drive. He misses to put any bat on the ball and Klaasen behind the wicket whips the bails off quickly and appeals. The umpire takes it upstairs and the replays shows Ashwin's back foot is not behind which means he has to depart. First wicket for Linde.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
SIX! In the slot for Umesh, he hammers it way over the mid-wicket fence. Wow, some hammering.
Fires one outside off, Umesh throws his bat but misses.

SIX! Number 4. Full ball in the slot outside off, Yadav hammers it over the mid off fielder. Nortje there attempts to push the ball back in play but the ball just evades him and goes over him and into the stands.
Wide outside off, Yadav goes for a massive heave but misses.
SIX! Raining sixes! In the slot again, Yadav lines himself up and clobbers it over the long on fence.

OUT! No fastest half century then. End of an entertaining innings nonetheless. A loopy ball this time, Yadav goes for the slog sweep but gets a top edge. The ball goes high in the air towards short fine leg. Klaasen calls it mine and pouches it nicely. Yadav departs but some hitting those. Linde has four on his debut.
On the pads, worked towards mid on for a single.
On the pads, blocked.
On the pads again, Nadeem paddles it fine for a single. First run in Test cricket.

SIX! Yadav goes but Shami is here and the hammering continues. A flighted ball around middle and leg, Shami dances down the track, gets to the pitch of the ball and hammers it way over the long on boundary.
FOUR BYES! Darts this one way down the leg side. Shami looks to pull but misses. The keeper misses too and the ball races to the fine leg fence.
Shortish length, worked towards mid on for a single.
Short ball outside the off stump line, Shami looks to guide this one towards third man but misses it completely.
Flighted ball outside off, Shami looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards first slip on the bounce. He played it with soft hands and that's why it did not go to hand.
The batsman gets a bottom edge of the bat on that one.
Flighted delivery around off, Shami defends it towards the point region. Nadeem wants a single but is sent back by Shami.
Full delivery outside off, Mohammed Shami pushes it towards the cover region and crosses over for a single. Good running from these two.
BEATEN! Flighted ball around the off stump, Nadeem wants to get into the act and looks to sweep but fails to put any bat on it.
Around off, pushed back to the bowler.
On off again, Shami taps it through point for a single.
Bouncer down the leg side. Nadeem ducks under it. Klaasen goes to his left and does well to pouch the ball. And Kohli calls the two batters back. INDIA DECLARE.

FOUR BYES! Poor delivery to start off with by Shami! Bowls a good length ball way down the leg side, Elgar lets it go. Saha dives to his right but does not reach it and the ball goes to fine leg fence.

OUT! CAUGHT! Excellent comeback delivery from Shami after bowling a poor first ball. Short of a length ball around off, Elgar is looking to leave the ball alone but is late in doing that. The ball hits the back of the bat and goes to Saha who takes a simple catch. Brilliant start for India here.
Bowls a bouncer now aimed at the body of Hamza who does well to duck under it.
BEAUTY! Shami is really steaming in now! Bowls a good length delivery around off, Hamza looks to defend but it goes between bat and pad into the keeper's gloves. Brilliant stuff.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Shami ends with a good length delivery down the leg side, Hamza lets it go to the keeper. Excellent over from Shami comes to an end. A wicket from it.
Umesh starts with a good length ball outside off, Quinton lets the ball go to the keeper.
Full delivery way outside the off stump line, de Kock sholders arms to this one.
Good length ball on the fourth stump line, de Kock does not fiddle with it and lets the ball go to the keeper.
Another one on a length outside off, Quinton lets the ball go to the keeper.
FOUR! Good shot from de Kock! Good length ball outside off, Quinton rocks back and pushes it towards the point region for a boundary. He is off the mark with that one.

OUT! CAUGHT! Snorter of a ball from Umesh Yadav! The experiment of sending Quinton opening does not work. Umesh Bowls a short delivery on the leg stump line, Quinton looks to take evasive action and it goes off the glove towards Saha who takes an excellent catch. Both the openers have been sent packing.
Flighted ball on middle, Hamza defends it off the front foot.
Played to the point region by the batsman.
Full delivery on off, Zubayr defends it off the front foot towards the off side.
Full delivery, driven towards mid off.
Outside off, left alone by Hamza.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Jadeja starts with a full toss outside the off stump line, Faf drives this towards the mid off region.
Another full toss outside off, Faf drives it towards the mid off region for a single. Umesh comes across and makes a good sliding stop. Faf gets off the mark with that single.
Flatter delivery on middle, Hamza defends it off the front foot to the bowler.
Short ball outside the off stump line, Zubayr punches this off the back foot towards cover.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Flighted ball on middle, Hamza defends it out.
Flighted ball on off, du Plessis defends it to silly point.
Floated ball on middle, du Plessis defends it back to the bowler.
Floated ball on off, Faf defends it to the off side.
Quicker delivery on the middle stump line, Faf gets his bat down in time and defends it out.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Floated ball on middle, Faf blocks it back to the bowler.
Starts with a good length ball on middle and leg, Hamza pushes it towards mid on.
Fullish delivery on middle, Zubayr lunges forward and defends it towards cover.
FOUR! Hamza gets off the mark with a boundary. Umesh bowls a full delivery on the pads, Zubayr flicks it off his pads towards the backward square leg region for a boundary. Good shot that.
Another full delivery on the pads, Hamza flicks it nicely towards deep square leg for three. Nadeem hares after it and makes an excellent sliding stop before it reaches the ropes.

OUT! BOWLED! What a ball from Umesh Yadav! After bowling two deliveries on the pads, gets this one to straighten after pitching it on a length on off.  Faf looks to defend it but it goes past the outside edge of his bat and hits the top of off stump, a fast bowler's delight. Excellent start for India on Day 3.
On a length on middle, Bavuma defends it towards mid on. Brilliant first over from Umesh Yadav.
Full delivery outside off, Hamza pushes it towards the cover region.
On a length on off, Zubayr rocks on his back foot and defends it to cover.
Good length delivery on middle, Hamza defends it off the back foot towards the off side.
Good length delivery angling into the batsman, Hamza flicks it towards square leg.
BOUNCER! Shami bowls this aimed at the body, Hamza ducks under it.
Good length ball outside off, Hamza leaves the ball go to the keeper.
EDGED AND FOUR! Full delivery on off, Bavuma looks to defend but it goes off his outside edge through gully and into the third man fence. Temba is off the mark with that.
Good length delivery on off, Bavuma defends it off the front foot towards cover.
Good length ball around off keeping low, Bavuma attempts to defend but it sneaks below his bat and into the keeper's gloves.
On a length on middle, Temba camps on his back foot and blocks it towards point.
Back of a length delivery outside off, Bavuma pushes it point and crosses over for a single.
Full delivery outside off, Hamza pushes it to cover for nothing.
On a length outside off, Bavuma is on his back foot and punches it to point.
Fullish delivery on the fourth stump line, Bavuma does not get tempted for the drive and shoulders arms to this one.
BEATEN! BEAUTIFUL BOWLING FROM SHAMI! Bowls a good length delivery around off, Bavuma attempts to defend it but it beats the outside edge and goes into the keeper's hands.
On a length on middle, Bavuma pushes it to point this time.
Full delivery around off, Bavuma pushes it towards cover.
FOUR! Nicely played from Bavuma! Short ball outside off, Temba rocks on his back foot and cuts it through the gully region and into the third man fence.

FOUR! Good shot! Short ball outside off, Hamza cuts it off the back foot towards backward point and Jadeja makes a run for it to save the boundary. He dives and tries to stop it but the ball rolls into the fence.
Fullish delivery on middle, Hamza defends it off the front foot towards mid-wicket.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Hamza pushes it towards mid on.
On a length on off, Zubayr rocks on his back foot and defends it towards cover.
EDGED AND FOUR! Excellent bowling this from Umesh. Bowls it on a length on middle squaring Hamza up but he gets an outside edge which goes through the gully fielder for a boundary.
