FOUR! Excellent shot this from Hamza. Umesh bowls this full on off, Hamza lunges forward and drives this through mid off for another boundary.
Back of a length delivery on off, Bavuma defends it off the back foot.
Good length delivery outside off, Bavuma does not fiddle with it and lets the ball go to the keeper.
Full delivery around off, Bavuma pushes it to cover region for a single.
Full delivery outside off, Zubayr drives it nicely towards the cover region and takes three. The fielder chases after it and cleans it up before it reaches the ropes.
Fullish delivery on off, Bavuma looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards mid-wicket.
On a length on the fourth stump line, Temba shoulders arms to this one.

OHH! This is brilliant bowling from Umesh Yadav. He bowls it on a length on middle, Zubayr looks to defend it but gets squared up and it goes off the outside edge towards first slip where it goes to Kohli on the bounce.
Back of a length delivery on middle, Hamza oushes it to the mid-wicket region for nothing.
Back of a length delivery outside off, Hamza puncxhes this off the back foot towards Agarwal at cover who misfields al;lowing the batsmen to take a single.
Good length delivery outside off, Temba pushes it towards the cover region.
On a length outside off, Bavuma guides it towards the gully region.
On a length on middle, Hamza defends it off the back foot towards the bowler.
Good length ball outside off, Hamza defends it off the back foot towards the cover region.
On middle, tucked towards mid-wicket.

FOUR! Shot of the morning so far! Umesh bowls a fullish delivery on middle, Hamza drives this beautifully down the ground and into the fence. Ashwin from mid off hares after it but fails to stop the ball.
FOUR! Nicely played! Good length ball around the off stump line, Hamza opens the face of the bat and guides this towards the third man region for another boundary. 50 up for the Proteas.
On middle, flicked towards the mid-wicket region.
Good length delivery on off, Hamza pushes it towards the point region for a single.

Full delivery on middle, Hamza pushes it towards the mid on region and takes off for a quick single. Umesh from mid on has as hy at the bowler's end but msses the stumps. Had he hit, it would have been close.
Played to mid-wicket region by the batsman.

FOUR BYES! Flighted ball outside off keeping low, Bavuma looks to defend but it misses the bat and it goes inbetween the legs off Saha and into the fence for four byes. Rare blemish for Wriddhiman behind the stumps.
BEATEN! Flighted delivery outside the off stump line, Temba looks to defend it but fails to put any bat on it.
Loopy ball on off, Bavuma attempts to defend it but it goes off the outside edge towards third man for a single.
Played through mid-wicket by the batsman.
Good length ball on middle, Bavuma rocks on his back foot and defends it to the mid-wicket region.
Outside off, Bavuma lets the ball go to the keeper.
Good length ball on middle, Bavuma looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards square leg. By the time, Jadeja cleans it up, the batters take a couple.

Good length ball outside off, Bavuma shoulders arms to this one. Saha fails to collect this ball cleanly as well but no harm done. Gavaskar on air, says that Saha might be nursing an injury and to protect that, he might be using that technique of keeping.
Fullish delivery outside off, Bavuma shoulders arms to this one.
Full delivery on middle, Temba flicks it towards the mid-wicket region.
Full delivery on middle, Hamza defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
Very full delivery around off, Hamza pushes it to point region for nothing.
FOUR! Nicely played! Floated ball outside off, Zubayr lunges forward and creams this past the cover fielder for a boundary.
The ball takes the outside edge goes towards the slip region. The batsmen have run through for a single.

FOUR! Bavuma shows some innovation here. Full delivery outside off, Bavuma goes for the reverse sweep and time sit well. The ball goes in between Mayank's legs at second slip and into the fine leg fence. 50-run partnership is between the two. Kohli is not happy as he looks at Mayank in an angry way.
Full delivery on middle, Temba defends it towards the bowler. Good over from South Africa.
On a length on middle, Hamza pushes it towards the mid-wicket fielder.

FOUR! Beautiful shot! Good length delivery outside off, Zubayr rocks on his back foot and drives this towards the cover region for another boundary. Hamza is looking very solid here and needs to make it big. He reaches his highest score in Tests with that.
Full delivery on middle, Hamza defends it out.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Full delivery on the pads, Hamza flicks this nicely off his pads towards mid-wicket for a couple. Ravindra Jadeja hares after it and stops it before it reaches the ropes.
Finally a bouncer is bowled by a seamer! Umesh bowls this aimed at the body, Hamza ducks under it.
BEATEN! Ashwin comes over the wicket this time and bowls a flighted ball outside off, Bavuma attempts to defend it but fails to put any bat on it.
Full delivery on middle, Temba defends it to the bowler.
Fullish delivery on middle, Temba pushes it to mid on and takes off for a quick single. Shami has a shy at the stumps but does so waywardly and the ball goes towards first slip.
Full delivery on middle, Hamza flicks it to mid-wicket.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.

SIX! Fifty for Hamza! He has looked good so far. Playing his first game in the series and makes an immediate impact. Ashwin bowls a flighted delivery on off, Hamza lofts this over the long on fielder for the first maximum of the innings.
Fuller ball around off, defended towards mid off.
FOUR! On the pads, Bavuma whips it through mid-wicket to get a boundary. Jadeja from short mid-wicket hares after the ball but the ball wins.
Around off, tapped towards cover this time.
Outside off, left alone.
Good length delivery around off, blocked off the back foot by Temba.
In the channel outside off, left alone.
Around off, pushed towards point off the outside edge.
Fuller ball this time, blocked towards mid off.
Fuller outside off, driven towards short extra cover. The fielder there makes a half stop as a single is taken.
That shoot off the surface, first one in the morning. Slightly fullish length around off and middle, Bavuma lunges forward to defense but the ball beats the outside edge and goes to the keeper.
The batsman has played it towards mid-wicket.
On middle, turned towards square leg.
Around off, a forward defense from Hamza.
Another forward defense from Hamza to this fuller ball around off.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
FOUR! Crunched! A short of a length ball outside off. Hamza rocks back and cuts it through point to get another boundary.
Slightly quicker and shorter, tapped right of Ashwin for a single through mid on.
Fuller ball outside off, Bavuma comes forward to defend but the ball takes the outside edge and goes towards third man. A couple taken.
Around off, blocked towards short leg.
On middle, it is kept away.
A quicker one which bounces a tad extra and turns away. Hamza looks to guide it through third man but misses.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
On middle, Hamza turns it towards mid-wicket off the inner half of the bat.
Fires this one outside off, Hamza lets it be.
Full ball around middle and leg, Bavuma comes down the track to work it towards mid-wicket but the ball hits the inner half of the bat and goes towards Jadeja at short fine leg.
On the pads, turned towards the leg side.
A quicker one outside off, Bavuma looks to drive but the ball whizzes past the outside edge.
Full outside off, Bavuma pushes it towards mid off.
Quicker ball again, Bavuma drives again but can't make any connection. No edge though so he will continue.
On middle and leg, eased  for a single towards mid on.
Loopy ball outside off, pushed towards covers.
A fuller ball this time, driven firmly but straight to the cover fielder.
WOW! That is some turn there. Jadeja lands it around off and middle, the ball turns away like a cobra and goes past the forward prod of the batter.
Around off, guided towards short third man.
Slightly short, driven towards mid off where Kohli dives to his left to save three there.
Loopy fuller ball, pushed towards covers.
FOUR! Full ball on middle, Bavuma gets in the position and sweeps it towards the fine leg fence. Nicely done.
Fuller length, it is kept away.
Shortish length, punched towards long for a single. 100 up for the Proteas.
Played to mid-wicket region by the batsman. They manage to come back for the second.
FOUR! Poor ball this one. Way outside off and on a shortish length, Hamza goes back and slaps it through point to get a boundary.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Around off, blocked.
Outside off, it is left alone.
Fuller outside off, pushed towards covers. Hamza wanted a run there but is send back.
A quicker one around off from Jadeja, Bavuma comes forward to block but the ball hits the pad first as the bat is behind the pad. The Indians appeal but not out says Nigel Llong. No reviews taken.
Fuller ball, pushed towards mid on for a single.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Full ball outside off, Bavuma tucks it towards point.
Flighted ball on off and middle, blocked back to the bowler.
A quicker ball on the pads, Bavuma looks to flick but is hit on the pads.
Flighted ball on off and middle, Bavuma comes down the track to work it towards the leg side but the ball hits him on the pads and lobs over the silly point fielder.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Quicker one, kept low too. Bavuma does well to block.
RJ darts a quicker one on the pads, Hamza looks to flick but misses to get hit on the pads.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.

NOT OUT! Missing the leg stump! India loose the review. Jadeja lands it around middle and leg, Hamza looks to defend it out but plays the wrong line to get hit on the pads. Jadeja appeals and then convinces his skipper to go for the review after the umpire calls it not out. Here comes the Ball Tracker, missing leg. India lose a review then.

OUT! Timber! Jadeja breaks the stand. An impressive innings comes to the end. A quicker one on a length which kept a little low, Hamza stays on the back foot to block but misses. The leg stump behind is disturbed.
Fuller ball around off, it is kept away.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Flatter ball around middle and leg, Bavuma looks to work it towards the leg side but misses to hit on the pads.

OUT! STUMPED! Nadeem gets his maiden Test wicket and what a delivery to remove the set batsman too. Nadeem gives the ball a lot of air and lands it around middle and leg, Bavuma comes down the track to defend. But the ball turns away as he plays it all around the ball to miss it. Saha behind the wicket collects the ball and whips the bails off. Two quick wickets for the Indians and the South African progress has been hampered.

Lands the ball way outside off and gets to turn the ball into the batter, Linde comes towards the off side to defend but the ball hits the flap of his pads and goes towards short third man. A mild appeal but not given.
Shortish length ball, Linde goes back and guides it towards third man to get three runs. George is off the mark in Test cricket with these runs.
Short ball this time, Klaasen goes back and punches it off the back foot through the point region. He is off the mark with a boundary.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Full ball on middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Around off, Linde keeps it out.
On off, pushed towards cover.

OUT? Not out says Rohit and Saha. Jadeja thinks its out. He is excited. He always is. Jadeja lands it around off, the ball goes straight as Linde comes forward to defend. The ball hits his back pad and Saha pouches it nicely and appeals. Umpire is unmoved. A correct call eventually.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Around off, it is kept away.
Around off and middle, Klaasen comes forward to defend it out.
Quicker delivery aimed at the pads, Klaasen looks to flick but misses it to get hit on the pads.
On the pads, turned towards the leg side for a single.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Full around off, Linde comes forward to keep it out.
Shortish length ball, punched towards covers.
Flighted ball around off, Klaasen comes forward and defends it out.
Shortish length, punched towards covers for a single.
Another short ball outside off, Linde this time stands tall and slaps it through cover-point for three runs before Umesh Yadav can get to to the ball.

OUT! Bowled 'em! Klaasen can't do much about that. A peach from SIR. Jadeja gives the ball a lot of flight and lands it around off, Klaasen comes forward to defend the ball but it turns away to beat the defense and goes on to hit the top of off stump.
Around off, pushed towards cover.
On middle and leg, Piedt looks to defend but the ball goes towards mid-wicket off the inner half of the bat for a run. Piedt is off the mark with that single.
Darts one on the pads, Piedt looks to work it down the leg side but misses. The ball hits his pad and goes towards short third man. A single taken.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
FOUR! Nicely done! Full ball on middle, Linde brings out the sweep and times it to perfection. The ball races to the deep mid-wicket fence.
The batsman rocks onto the back foot and punches the ball.
Around off and middle, worked towards mid on.
Outside off, blocked.
Flighted ball on middle and leg, Piedt defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
Full delivery outside off, Dane lunges forward and drives it past the mid off fielder for a couple. Kohli from mid off runs after it and cleans it up.
Floated ball on middle, Dane defends it towards the point region.
That ball has taken the inside edge onto the pads.
Quicker delivery on the middle stump line, Piedt gets his bat down in time and defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted ball on off, Piedt drives it towards the mid off region for nothing.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde comes on his front foot and defends it back to the bowler.
Flatter delivery on middle, George defends it off the back foot.
Full delivery on middle, George defends it out.
NO BALL! Nadeem oversteps. Flighted ball on middle, Linde defends it off the front foot towards the bowler. Replays show that Nadeem was just over the line.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Full delivery on middle, Linde defends it out to the bowler.
Short ball on middle, George is solid in defense.
Loopy ball on middle, Piedt looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards square leg. He takes a single.
Short ball on middle, George defends it of the back foot towards the bowler.
Full delivery on middle, George defends it off the front foot.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Floated ball on middle, George Linde defends it to short leg off the front foot.
Loopy delivery on middle, George defends it out and goes into LUNCH ON DAY 3 unbeaten.
Starts with a good length ball outside off, Piedt plays it off his back foot towards point.
Good length ball around off keeping low, Piedt looks to defend but it sneaks below his bat and hits Saha on his thumb. He looks in pain but seems fine to continue.
BEATEN! On a length outside off, Piedt attempts to defend yet again but fails to put any bat on it.

OUT! LBW! Piedt has to make the long walk back to the pavilion. Excellent bowling this from Shami this. Bowls this on a length on middle and leg which kept a little low, Piedt looks to flick but misses it to get hit on the pads. The Indian players appeal and the umpire gives it out. Piedt does not even wait to ask his partner for a review and walks back. The Ball Tracker shows that it was umpire's call on hitting the leg stump.
Good length ball outside off, Rabada looks to defend it but it goes off the bottom edge towards first slip.
Bouncer! The batsman ducks in time to let that one go over him.
Flighted ball on off, Linde pushes it towards covers and takes a single.
Flighted ball on off, Rabada defends it back to the bowler.
Flatter delivery on middle and leg, Rabada looks to defend but it hits the back pad.
Full delivery on off, Rabada drives it to mid off.

OUT! RUN OUT! Bull's eye from Umesh Yadav! Never run on a misfield says Sunil Gavaskar on air. Rabada drives this towards mid off where Umesh slides to make the stop but he misfields. Rabada sees that and looks to take the run. Umesh recovers, gets to the ball and fires a throws  at the non-striker's end. Direct hit it is, Rabada has to depart. He looks at the heavens as he walks back to the pavilion. The umpire does not even go to the third umpire to check as Kagiso was well out. Excellent piece of fielding.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde defends it to short leg.

Excellent bouncer from Shami! Bowls it aimed at the body, Nortje looks to fend it away but gets hit on the gloves before going on to hit the shoulder. That was nasty. Nortje looks in pain. Shami asks whether he is fine to which he responds that he is fine to continue.
Another bouncer from Shami! He bowls this aimed at the body, Anrich looks to fend it away but it hits the edge of the bat and into the pitch. Brilliant bowling this from Mohammed.
LEG BYE! Shami bowls this full delivery on the pads, Anrich looks to flick but it hits the pads and goes towards the fine leg region for a leg bye.
BEATEN! Good length ball outside off, Linde looks to defend but he fails to put any bat on it.
The batsman plays the pull-shot. One run added to the total.
Good length ball outside off, Nortje defends it towards the slip cordon.

FOUR! Just goes over the mid on fielder. Flighted ball on middle, Linde dances down the track and lofts this over the mid on fielder for a boundary. Nadeem jumps to catch the ball but it just goes over the head of him.
Flighted ball on middle, George defends it to silly point.
Flighted ball on the pads, Linde looks to flick but gets hit on the pads.
Flatter delivery on middle, Linde looks to defend but it hits the thigh pad but no harm is done.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards square leg.
On a length on middle, Anrich defends this off the back foot.

Back of a length delivery around off angling into the batsman, Nortje looks to fend it away while jumping in the air but it hits him on the elbow and goes towards first slip. Anrich looks is some pain out there and has called for the physio.
Full delivery outside off, Nortje looks to drive but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards the mid on fielder for nothing.
Short ball on the off stump line, Nortje this time fends it away while jumping towards short leg.
Good length ball outside the off stump line, Anrich defends it to point.
Short ball on middle, Nortje looks to defend it out and it goes off the bottom edge onto his pads and into the pitch.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde defends it back to the bowler.
OHH! Flighted ball outside off, George comes down the track to loft it over mid off but gets an inside edge onto his pads. That probably saved him as had he missed it he would have been stumped.

NOT OUT! Linde survives! Flighted ball on the middle and leg stump line, Linde looks to flick it away but gets hit on the pads. The Indians appeal but the umpire is unmoved. Ashwin convinces his skipper for the review. The Ultra Edge rolls in and there is no bat involved. Ball Tracker rolls in and it shows that it is missing the leg stump. India lose both their reviews.

Another flighted delivery on the pads, George looks to flick but gets hit on the pads again. The Indians appeal again but the umpire gives it not out. This looked closer and the replays show that it was clipping the leg stump.
FOUR! Nicely played! Flighted ball on middle, Linde lunges forward and lofts this wide of the mid-wicket fielder for a boundary. Vital runs these.
The batsman has driven it straight down the ground.
On a length on middle, Anrich defends it off the back foot towards the leg side.
Good length delivery on middle, Anrich flicks it to the square leg region for nothing.
Good length delivery on middle, Nortje looks to flick but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards the deep square leg region. By the time the fielder comes around, the batters take a couple.
Good length ball on middle, Anrich defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery outside off, Nortje drives it to the mid off fielder for nothing.

Good length ball on the middle and leg stump line, Nortje looks to flick but gets hit high on the pads. Shami and the rest appeal but nothing from the umpire. India cannot opt for the review as they have no review left. Well, there was an inside edge which the Ultra Edge confirmed, so the DRS would've gone against the Indians anyway.
Flatter delivery on middle, Linde defends it off the front foot.
Loopy ball on middle, Linde defends it out.
Floated ball around off, Linde defends it towards the point region.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Fullish delivery outside the off stump line, Linde pushes it towards long off and takes a single.
Ashwin bowls this with a bit of air around off, Nortje lunges forward and defends it towards the point region.
SIX! Excellent use of the feet! Flighted ball on off, Linde dances down the track and lofts this over the long on fielder for a maximum.

DROPPED! Saha is the culprit! Flighted ball around off, Linde looks to defend it off the back foot but gets an outside edge towards Saha who can't hold onto it cleanly. Saha has looked rusty behind the stumps. Maybe, the injury is hampering his keeping skills.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde flicks it towards the leg side for a single.
Floated ball outside off, Nortje lets the ball go to the keeper.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Low full toss outside off, Linde prods forward and pushes it towards the cover region for a single.
Full delivery on middle and leg, Nortje looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards mid-wicket. The batters take a single.
Full delivery on middle, George defends it back to the bowler.
Floated ball on middle, Linde blocks it out.
Loopy ball outside off, Linde looks to defend it but it goes off the outside edge towards point for a single.
Loopy ball outside off, Nortje defends it towards the point region.
OHH! Flighte delivery landing in the rough which spun into the batsman, Linde looks to defend but he misses it and just misses the off stump. Saha does really well to collect that one.

What happened there? It was another flighted ball outside off landing on the rough, Linde looks to slog sweep this one but he misses it. Saha does not collect it cleanly and it goes to Rahane at first slip. Nadeem was seen telling Rahane to get the batsman run out as he was out of the crease.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde flicks it towards the leg side for a single.
Flighted delivery outside off, Nortje leaves the ball alone.
Floated ball on middle, Anrich flicks it towards square leg for nothing.
Full delivery on off, George defends it to cover.
Loopy ball on off, George defends it towards the off side and takes a single.
Bowls a flighted ball outside off, left alone by Nortje.
Flighted ball on middle, Nortje defends it off the front foot.
Quicker delivery on middle keeping low, Nortje gets his bat down in time and flicks it towards square leg for a single.
Loopy ball on middle, George defends this of the front foot towards the bowler.
Lands it around middle, Nortje comes forward to block but hits the pad and goes towards the leg side.
Beautiful bowling! Nadeem gives the ball a lot of flight and gets it to turn away from the forward prod of Nortje.
A quicker one on middle and leg, Nortje does well to flick it towards mid-wicket.
This time he covers the line of this ball to dead-bat it onto the pitch.
On off, a shortish length too, Nortje rocks back and blocks it off the back foot.
On the pads, turned towards short leg.
Full delivery around off, Linde lunges forward and drives this past Jadeja towards long off and takes a single.
Flatter delivery on middle, Nortje flicks it towards the mid-wicket for nothing.
Flighted ball on middle, Nortje defends it off the front foot.
Loopy ball on middle, Nortje attempts to defend but it goes off the inside half towards square leg.
Flatter delivery on middle, Nortje flicks it towards the leg side for nothing.
Fullish delivery on middle, Anrich defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted ball on middle and leg, Linde looks to flick it but gets hit on the pads. The Indians appeal but nothing from the umpire. It looked like it was going down the leg side.
Full delivery outside off, Linde drives this towards the mid off region and crosses over for a single.
Floated ball on middle, Nortje defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
Flatter delivery on the middle stump line, Anrich defends it back to the bowler off the back foot.
Another flat delivery around off, Anrich defends it out.
Flat delivery outside off which spun a mile, Linde looks to defend but it hits the pads and rolls towards the square leg region. Jadeja appeals but nothing from the umpire.
Floated ball outside off, Linde plays it towards point and takes a single.
Outside off, left alone.
Flighted delivery on middle, Anrich flicks it towards the mid-wicket region.
BEATEN! Beautiful delivery by Jadeja! Floated ball outside off, Nortje looks to defend but fails to put any bat on it.
BEATEN! Loopy ball outside off, Nortje looks to defend it again but misses the ball completely.
Carromball outside the off stump line, Linde rocks on his back foot and cuts it towards the point region.
Flighted ball on the pads, Linde looks to flick but it goes off his pads towards the leg side for a single.
Flighted ball on middle, Anrich defends it off the front foot and into the ground.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Floated ball on middle, Anrich defends it off the front foot.
On middle, defended off the middle.
BEATEN! Starts with a good length delivery outside off, Linde goes for an expansive drive but fails to put any bat on it.
Good length ball outside off, Linde does not fiddle with it and leaves the ball alone.
Full delivery outside off, Linde pushes this towards the cover fielder.
BEATEN! Another expansive drive from Linde! Umesh bowls a good length delivery outside off, Linde goes for the drive but misses it completely.
Umesh comes around the wicket and bowls a back of a length delivery on middle, Linde looks to defend but it goes off the gloves and onto the pitch.
Good length ball on off, Linde looks to defend but it goes off the inside half of his bat towards the fine leg region for a single.
Around off and middle, Linde comes forward to defend.
Fires this one outside off, Linde pushes it towards point to change ends.
Flights this on middle, tucked towards mid-wicket.
On middle, Nortje lunges forward to work it towards the leg side.
On the stumps again, Nortje keeps it out.

Almost! But almost! Nadeem lands it around middle and gets the ball to turn away just a hint. Nortje comes forward to defend but the ball goes past the outside edge. Wasn't too far away from the off pole.

OUT! CAUGHT AT SLIP! Umesh is the man who breaks the stubborn stand. Dishes a full ball outside off, asking Linde to go for the drive. He obliges, manages a thick outside edge which goes straight to Rohit Sharma at second slip.
Back of a length ball on middle and leg stump line, Ngidi blocks it off the back foot.
Bouncer! Ngidi does well to duck under it.
Another bouncer! This time Ngidi is not sure if he wants to duck or play at it. He
Full ball on the stumps, Ngidi blocks it out.
The batsman shows the full face of the bat and defends the ball off the back foot.
Around off, Nortje goes back and defends it out.

OUT! LBW! Nadeem has two. Nadeem bowls a flatter ball on middle, skids in slightly. Nortje looks to defend but is late as the ball hits him on the pads. Nadeem appeals and the umpire raises the fingers. Norje opts for the review immediately but it won't help him. No edge there confirms the Ultra Edge  and the Ball Tracker confirms three reads. SOUTH AFRICA ALL OUT ON 162.

EDGED AND FOUR! What is de Kock doing, playing such a wide delivery. It is the first ball of the innings. Shami lands a fuller ball outside off, de Kock is glued to his crease and throws his bat at the ball. A thick inside edge is produced which flies over the slip cordon and into the third man fence.
Outside off, this time de Kock watches the ball go to the keeper.
Another length ball in the channel, de Kock lets it be.
Goes over the wicket and bowls a back of a length ball angling away. De Kock sways away from it.
On the pads on a good length, de Kock tucks it towards the leg side for a quick run.
Another bouncer outside off, Elgar evades it by dropping his wrists.

OUT! TIMBER! What a jaffa first up! The off stump is uprooted. Quinton de Kock shakes his head as he goes back to the pavilion. Lands the ball on off and middle, de Kock comes forward to defend but he plays the wrong line. The ball came in and hit the pad and then went on to demolish the off pole. What a start for the Indians.
On the pads, Hamza keeps it out.
Full ball around off, Hamza drives it uppishly to the left of Umesh. The ball goes towards mid off.
Another bouncer! But this just does not rise. Hamza ducks under it but the ball goes to Saha on the bounce and he can't gather it. A bye taken.
And another bouncer! Elgar keeps it out.

FOUR! Good length ball on middle and leg, the ball came in sharply. Elgar looks to work it on the leg side but the ball takes the inside edge, hits the pads and flies between the third slip and gully fielder.
On the leg side this time, Hamaza lets it be.
Outside off, left alone.

OUT! Stumps are shattered once again. Indian pacers are on fire. The half centurion of the first inning departs for a duck. Full length ball, shaping away from the forward prod of Hamza. The ball beats the outside edge and goes to destroy the stumps behind. South Africa are two down.
Fullish length on the pads, Faf works it towards fine leg for a single to get off the mark.
Full on the stumps again, Elgar defends it out.
Bouncer outside off, Elgar sways away.
On the pads of Faf on a fullish length, he flicks it through square leg and runs three before the fielder can get to the ball and return it back to the keeper.
On middle, Elgar pushes it towards mid on off the back foot.
Outside off, it is left alone.
Beaten! Yadav gets closer to the off pole on a shortish length. Elgar looks to defend but the ball whizzes past the outside edge. That kept a hint low too.
Good length ball on the pads, tucked towards mid-wicket for a run.
In the channel outside off, Faf shoulders arms.
Shortish length ball on off, Elgar stands tall to defend it out.
Fullish length on the stumps, Elgar keeps it out.
A bouncer now! Elgar ducks under it.
On middle, Elgar tucks it towards short mid-wicket.
Comes around the wicket and bowls a fullish length outside off, Elgar pushes it towards covers and takes a quick single.
Full ball outside off, Faf makes a leave to get through the over.
On the stumps on a good length, Elgar drives it straight to mid on.
On middle and leg, blocked off the back foot.
Back of a length ball this time, Elgar ducks under it.
Good length ball closer to the off pole, Elgar looks to defend but does so with the bottom part of the willow.
Full on the pads again, worked straight to Jadeja at mid-wicket.
Good length outside off, Elgar taps it through cover-point. He had played it with the soft hands there, Faf wanted two but Elgar says no. Nadeem there fumbles and they eventual get the second run.
Beaten! In the channel outside off on a good length, Faf is rooted to his crease as he hangs hit bat to see the ball whizz past his bat.
On the stumps again, Faf keeps it out.
Full ball on the off pole line, pushed towards covers.
Full on the pads this time, flicked firmly but can't beat Agarwal at mid-wicket.
Outside off, du Plessis defends it out.

OUT! LBW! Hitting the stumps. The skipper is out of here. Good length ball  angling away from the batter. Faf looks to defend it out but is beaten as the ball jags back in. It hits the pads, Shami and the Indians belt out an appeal. The umpire agrees. The Protea skipper consults Elgar and goes for the DRS. Well, keep walking, Mr. Skipper because there is no edge and three reds it is which is confirmed by the Ultra Edge and the Ball Tracker. Skipper gone, takes one review with him too. South Africa in tatters, in the second innings too.
FOUR! Good length ball outside off, Elgar reaches out for the ball and drives it through cover-point to get a boundary.
Around off, guided towards third man.
Fuller ball outside off, drives to the cover fielder.
Bouncer this time, Elgar ducks under it.
What a bouncer now! Yadav bends his back and bowls this around middle and off. Elgar looks to sway away but is hit on the right shoulder. That would've hurt.
Good length ball around off, jags back in sharply. Elgar looks to flick but misses to get hit on the pads. A muted appeal but this looked to be missing leg.
Good length ball outside off, Bavuma shoulders arms to this one.
Good length ball on off, Bavuma rocks on his back foot and defends it towards the cover region.

OUT! CAUGHT! Shami gets his third wicket of the innings and continues his tradition of bowling well in the second innings. Excellent bowling this from him. Bowls it on a length around off angling away from the batsman, Bavuma looks to push at it with no feet movement but gets a thick outside edge towards Saha who takes a catch diving forward. India inch closer and closer to victory.
Good length ball on middle, Klaasen defends it off the back foot.
Another short delivery on off, Klaasen defends it off the back foot towards the off side.
Full delivery outside off, Heinrich drives it towards the cover region.
FOUR! Nicely done! Good length ball outside off, Elgar directs it through the gully and the point region. The ball races to the third man fence.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.

Ouch! Straight on the helmet. Elgar goes down straightaway. A back of a length ball, Elgar took the eyes off the ball early and the ball thuds on the helmet. He immediately goes down. The Indians show concern as they quickly come towards the batter. Not looking good as long as Elgar is concerned.
Starts with a full delivery outside off, Linde drives this towards short cover for nothing.
On a length on middle, Linde rocks on his back foot and defends it back to the bowler.
Back of a length delivery outside off keeping low, Linde looks to defend but it sneaks under his bat and goes to the keeper.
Full delivery on middle, Klaasen defends it back to the bowler.
Good length ball outside off, Heinrich attempts to defend but gets an outside edge towards third man for a couple. The fielder runs after it and cleans it up.
Good length ball outside the off stump line, Klaasen shoulders arms to this one.
Fullish delivery outside off, Klaasen pushes it off the front foot towards the mid off region for nothing.
Full delivery outside off, Klaasen drives this beautifully towards extra cover  where Jadeja makes a good diving stop. It is cleaned up by Ashwin at mid off. The batters take a single.
Good length ball on middle, Linde flicks it off his back foot towards the mid-wicket region for nothing.
Full delivery on middle, Klaasen defends it towards mid on.
Floated ball on middle, Klaasen defends it back to the bowler.
Floated delivery on middle, defended back to Jadeja.
It's been driven superbly through the covers.
Loopy ball on middle and leg, Klaasen lunges forward and defends it to mid-wicket.
Full delivery on middle, Klaasen defends it out.
Good length ball on off, Linde opens the face of his bat and guides it towards the point region.
BEATEN! Back of a length delivery outside the off stump line, Linde looks to cut it but fails to make any connection on it.
Shami comes over the wicket and bowls a full delivery on middle, Linde pushes it back to the bowler.
Short ball aimed at the body, Linde does well to duck under it.
Full delivery around off, Linde pushes this to the extra cover region.

BEATEN! Good bowling from Shami! Bowls a full delivery outside off, Linde looks to drive it but gets beaten. Shami appeals but nothing from the umpire. Someone from the Indian camp shouts that there was bat involved but Shami is not willing to listen.
Flighted delivery on middle, Klaasen pushes it towards the bowler where Jadeja gets a hand on it. The ball rolls towards mid on for nothing.
Flighted delivery on middle, Klaasen blocks it out.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Full delivery outside off, Heinrich drives this towards the cover region.
On middle, defended off the front foot.
Flighted delivery on middle, Klaasen defends it back towards mid on.
Good length ball on off, Linde defends it towards cover.
FOUR! Beautiful shot from Linde. He gets off the mark with a boundary. Short ball way outside off, George stands back and punches this towards the cover region.
Good length delivery down the leg side, Linde flicks it towards the fine leg fielder and crosses over for a single.
The ball strikes the batsman very low on the pads.
Good length delivery on the pads, Klaasen flicks it towards the square leg region for a couple.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Full delivery on middle, Linde defends it off the back foot towards the bowler.
Another full delivery on middle, Linde plays it back to the bowler off the front foot.
Flighted ball outside off, George defends it towards the point region.
Flighted ball on middle, Linde defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on middle again, George defends it back to the bowler.

OUT! LBW! Klaasen is the latest casualty to make his way back to the pavilion. Brilliant delivery from Umesh though. Good length ball on the off stump line, angling in to the batsman, Klaasen looks to flick it towards the leg side but gets hit on the pads. The Indian players appeal and Nigel Llong gives it out immediately. Klaasen consults his partner regarding the review and decides not to take the review. Good decision in the end as the Ball Tracker shows that it was going on to hit the leg stump.
Good length delivery on middle, Piedt defends it out.

Good length ball on middle, Dane flicks it towards the mid-wicket region.
On a length outside off keeping low, Piedt looks to defend but misses the ball completely due to the low bounce on it.
Good length ball down the leg side, Piedt looks to flick but misses.
Flighted ball outside off keeping low, Linde looks to defend but it goes past the outside edge of his bat and goes to the keeper. Excellent take behind the stumps by Saha.
Yorker around the off stump, Linde gets his bat down in time and blocks it out.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Full delivery on middle, Linde flicks it towards mid-wicket.

Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.

Full delivery on middle, Piedt defends it out.
Another flighted delivery on middle, Dane defends it out.
FOUR! Almost a catch at mid off. A fuller ball outside off from Umesh, Linde checks his drive, the ball lands just short of the mid off fielder and goes between his legs for a boundary to long off.
FOUR! Beautiful shot! Good length delivery on the pads, Linde flicks it nicely towards the deep mid-wicket region for another boundary. 50 up for the visitors.
Good length ball on middle, Linde flicks it towards the mid-wicket region.
Good length delivery outside off, Linde drives this crisply towards Mayank at cover on the bounce. Agarwal looks in pain after that shot as it hit him flush on the palm.
Short ball down the leg side, Linde looks to pull it but fails to put any bat on it. Saha collects it while jumping in the air.
Short ball outside off, Linde pushes it towards the cover region.

SIX! Brilliant use of the feet from Piedt. Flighted delivery on middle, Piedt dances down the track and lofts this straight over the bowler's head for a maximum.
Short ball on off, Piedt pulls it towards the mid-wicket region for a single.

FOUR! Flighted ball on middle, Linde  lofts it towards the mid-wicket region for a boundary.
On a length on off, Piedt looks to defend it but gets an inside edge onto his pads. No harm done though.
Good length ball outside off, Piedt looks to defend but it goes off the outside edge towards the slip cordon on the bounce.

Good length delivery outside off, Dane guides it towards the point region where Nadeem makes an excellent diving stop. Stops the batsmen from taking the single.
Short ball outside off spinning into the batsman, Linde looks to cut but it goes off the inside edge towards  id on.
Flighted ball on middle, George defends it off the back foot.
Short ball on middle, George rocks on his back foot and defends it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball outside off, George Linde comes down the track and drives this towards the mid off region for a single.
OHH! Flighted ball on the middle stump line, Piedt looks to pull it but it goes off the inside edge onto his pad and towards fine leg for a single. Saha was appealing but nothing from the uumpire.
The batsman defends it from within the crease.
Good length ball outside off, Piedt defends it towards the point region and wants a single but is sent back.
On a length on off, Dane defends it off the back foot towards point.
On off, defended off the back foot.
Full delivery on middle, Piedt flicks it to one of the two short mid-wicket fielders.
Full delivery on off, Piedt defends it back to the bowler.
Good length delivery outside off, Dane Piedt defends it off the back foot towards the cover region.
Flatter delivery outside off, Linde pushes it towards cover.
Flighted ball around off, Linde comes down the track and pushes it to long on and takes a single.
Short ball outside off, Dane cuts it towards point where Ashwin makes a diving stop.
Flighted ball on off, Dane defends it to extra cover.
Flatter delivery outside off, Dane cuts it towards the point fielder.
BEATEN! Flighted delivery outside off, Piedt looks to play the slog sweep but fails to make any connection to it.
Ashwin starts with a ball firing outside off, the ball hits the cracks and keeps low. The ball goes behind, Saha looks to collect but the ball hits ring finger. He is down in  pain.
Around off, tapped towards silly point.
Flighted ball outside off, Linde goes for the drive but the ball takes the leading edge and goes towards point uppishly. A single taken.
Around off, blocked easily by Piedt.
Shortish length on off, Piedt goes back on his back foot to defend.
On the pads, turned towards short mid-wicket.
Flighted ball around off, Linde comes down the track to push it back to the bowler.
Around off, pushed towards cover-point and a quick single taken.
On middle, Piedt hangs back on the back foot to punch it towards mid on.
On middle, it is blocked nicely.
On the stumps again, Piedt is solid behind the line of the ball to defend again.
Flighted ball around off, driven to mid off.
Fires one outside off, Linde stays back to turn it towards point.
On off, Linde keeps it out.

OUT! Direct hit from Nadeem. A quicker ball from Ashwin, Linde turns it behind square and takes off for a run. He then stops for a nano second and then again starts running at the non-striker's end. Nadeem gets to the ball, fires the throw and hits the stumps to find Linde short. South Africa six down.
On middle, pushed towards mid-wicket.
Outside off, blocked towards point.
Outside off, slightly shortish length. Piedt goes back to cut but misses to put any bat on ball.
Full delivery on middle, de Bruyn defends it back to the bowler.
Outside off, left alone by Theunis.

FOUR! MISFIELD! Short ball outside the off stump line, Theunis cuts it towards the point region where Ashwin dives but is unable to stop the ball. It goes through his hands and it rolls towards the deep point fence. He gets off the mark with that.
Short ball on middle, de Bruyn pushes it off the back foot.
FOUR! Nicely played! Flighted ball on middle, de Bruyn lunges forward and whips it towards the mid-wicket region for a boundary.
Flighted ball on middle, Theunis defends it out to the bowler.
On middle, tucked towards short mid-wicket.
Around off, Piedt blocks it out.
On middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Quicker one outside off, pushed towards cover-point.
The batsman has flicked the ball off his pads.
FOUR! Poor ball from Ashwin. Short and way outside off, Piedt stays on his back foot and drives it through covers for a boundary. No real chase from Pujara there.
Full on off, drives straight to mid off.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
On off, de Bruyn comes forward to block it out.
Fuller again, pushed to covers.
SIX! Flighted ball on middle, de Bruyn dances down the track to get to the pitch of the delivery and loft it over the bowler's head for a maximum.
The batsman has played that off the front foot and into the ground.
Around off, pushed back to the bowler.
Short outside off, punched to point.
On off, kept out nicely by Piedt.
On the pads this time, Piedt whips it right of Jadeja at square leg for a couple of runs before Jadeja chases down the ball.
Around off, Piedt blocks it coming forward.
Flighted ball on middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Fuller around off, eased through mid off for a run.
Outside off, worked towards point.
Goes past the outside edge this time. Jadeja lands it around middle and leg and gets the ball to turn a hint away to beat the outside edge.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Flighted ball on off, pushed through mid off for a run.
Fires it outside off, de Bruyn lets it be. Wasn't too far from the stumps.
Full outside off, drives straight to mid off.
Outside off, Piedt looks to defend but does so with an inside edge. The ball hits his pads then.
On off, turns into the batter sharply. Piedt looks to work it down the leg side but is late in doing so. The ball goes to hit him high on the pads.
Defended off the back foot by the batsman.
On off, Piedt keeps it out.
Flatter ball around off, Piedt keeps it out with a defensive shot.
Quicker one on the pads, turned towards square leg for a single.
FOUR! Flighted ball on middle, Piedt goes across the left side and lofts it over mid on for a boundary.
Another quicker ball on the pads, Piedt turns it with the spin towards fine leg. Umesh chases the ball and stops but the batters take three.
Tossed up around middle, pushed towards mid on.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
On middle, de Bruyn looks to paddle sweep but manages just a bottom edge.
Flighted ball outside off, worked towards point.
Outside off again, driven straight to the cover region.
Shortish length, Piedt hangs on the back foot to defend it out.
The batsman has played it to the point region.
Flighted ball around off, pushed towards the bowler.

Loopy ball around off, turns into the batter, who looks to drive. He misses to make any connection, the ball hits the back pad and lobs straight to Rahane at second slip. A mild appeal but nothing serious.
Short ball outside off, de Bruyn guides it towards the gully region for nothing.
Flighted ball on middle, Theunis flicks it towards the mid-wicket region for a single.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.

OUT! BOWLED! Piedt falls off a poor shot! Quicker ball on middle and leg, Piedt dances down the track and looks to slog it towards the mid-wicket region but misses the ball completely. The ball goes on to hit the leg stump. India three wickets away from a whitewash.
Full delivery outside off, Rabada defends it towards the point region.

OHH! Flighted ball around off, Rabada looks to defend but it hits the pads. There is a stifled appeal for LBW but nothing from the umpire. Jadeja is seen signalling that the ball was probably going down the leg side.
Outside off, de Bruyn looks to cut but the ball turns in to beat the bat.
Lands it around off does Ashwin, de Bruyn comes forward to defend but the ball takes an inside edge onto the pads.
On the pads, glanced towards fine leg for a couple.
FOUR! Around off this time, de Bruyn connects his reverse sweeps it towards the third man fence. 100 up for South Africa.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
On the pads, turned towards short mid-wicket.

FOUR BYES! Pant can't gather that one. Flighted ball outside off, probably lands in a crack and turns in sharply to beat the drive of Rabada. It sneaks through Pant's gloves and goes to the fine leg fence.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Outside off, Rabada lines himself up for a slog but misses.
Outside off again, this time Rabada keeps it out.
FOUR! Over mid on! Rabada is off the pair. Full delivery outside off, Kagiso looks to slog it away but it goes of the toe-end of the bat towards the mid-wicket region for a boundary.
The batsman has punched the ball off the back foot.
Outside off, de Bruyn comes forward to defend but misses. The ball goes to Saha, beating the outside edge.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
On the pads, turned towards mid-wicket for a single.
Outside off, turned towards point off the outer half of the bat.
FOUR! Fuller ball outside off, Rabada gets to the pitch of the ball by lunging forward and hammers it through covers to get his second boundary.
Flatter ball this time, blocked off the back foot.
Full ball outside off, pushed towards cover.
Slightly short, turned towards point.
Quicker one on the pads, turned towards short fine leg.
Outside off on a fullish length, driven straight to covers.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.
On middle, de Bruyn keeps it out.
On the pads, pushed towards mid on.
Quicker one, Rabada manages to get the bat in time to defend it out.

FOUR! Flighted ball outside off, Rabada goes for slog sweep but the ball takes the outside edge and lobs uppishly wide of Jadeja. The ball races towards the third man fence. Jadeja hares after the ball but eventually can't keep it in play.
The batsman has defended it by getting right behind the line of the delivery.

OUT! Caught! This time Rabada finds Jadeja at backward point. Finally a wicket for Ashwin. Another flighted ball on middle, turning away. Rabada goes for the slog again but again finds a thick outside edge. The ball lobs and lands straight in the pouch of Jadeja. India two wickets away from a whitewash.
On off, Nortje comes forward to defend it out.

NOT OUT! Shortish length ball outside off, de Bruyn looks to cut it off the back foot but can't make any connection. Pant behind the wicket pouches the ball and appeals along with Jadeja. Not out says the umpire but Jadeja looks convinced. Kohli after a chat with Rahane and Pant goes for the review. Let's see what the replays show. No edge, shows the Ultra Edge. De Bruyn survives.
Another beauty! Lands on middle and leg and makes it turn away. De Bruyn comes forward to defend but the ball beats the outside edge.
Defended off the front foot by the batsman presenting the full face of the bat.
Fuller ball outside off, pushed towards mid off for a run.
FOUR! On the pads of Nortje, he tickles it fine down the leg side. Umesh Yadav gives it a chase but the ball wins the race.
Full on middle, turned towards mid on.
Full delivery on middle, Theunis defends it off the front foot towards the bowler.
Flighted ball outside off, de Bruyn pushes it wide of mid off and takes a single.
Flighted ball on middle, Nortje defends it with a big stride forward.
Flighted ball outside off, Nortje goes for the slog sweep but fails to put any bat on it. Poor shot though with only three balls left in the day.
Flighted ball on middle, Nortje flicks it towards the fine leg region for a single.
FOUR! Excellent shot from de Bruyn. Flighted ball outside off, de Bruyn plays a slog sweep towards the deep square leg region for a boundary.
Full delivery on middle, Nortje defends it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on middle, Nortje tries to flick it but gets an inside edge towards the square leg region.
Flatter delivery on middle, Anrich defends it off the back foot.
Full delivery around off, Anrich pushes it towards the cover region.
Floated ball outside the off stump line, Anrich lets the ball go to the keeper.
Full delivery on the middle stump line, Anrich defends it back to the bowler.
Starts with a good length ball on middle, Theunis defends it towards the mid-wicket region.
LEG BYE! Good length ball on the middle and leg stump line, de Bruyn looks to pull it but gets hit on the pads. The ball goes towards square leg for a leg bye.
Short delivery on middle, Nortje rocks on his back foot and defends it towards short leg.
Fullish delivery on off, Nortje defends it towards the cover region for nothing.
Short ball on middle, Nortje rocks on his back foot and pushes it towards short leg.
BEATEN! Excellent delivery from Shami! Good length delivery around off, Nortje attempts to defend it but fails to put any bat on it.
Nadeem starts with a flighted delivery on middle and leg, de Bruyn defends it off the front foot towards the leg side.
Flighted ball on the leg stump line, Theunis looks to flick it but gets hit on the pads.
Flighted delivery outside off, de Bruyn defends it towards the cover region.
Flighted delivery on off, de Bruyn pushes it towards the cover region.

OUT! CAUGHT! Excellent keeping from Saha here. This is the reason that Kohli regards him as the best wicketkeeper in the country. Flatter delivery outside off which kept very low, Theunis looks to cut this one but it goes off the bottom edge towards Saha. He bends down and takes an excellent catch. The umpire gives it out immediately. One more wicket to go for the Indians to wrap up the series.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! India finish the game off in just two overs to end the series with a whitewash and it has happened in an unusual manner. Full delivery on off, Ngidi drives this towards the mid on region but it hits Nortje flush on the wrists and lobs up in the air. Nadeem catches it off the rebound and it is given out. Nortje looks in serious pain out there. The Indian players check on him whether he is fine or not. INDIA WIN THE MATCH BY AN INNINGS AND 202 RUNS.
